"TIU akademik mukammallik bo'yicha Markaziy Osiyoda yuqori reytingga erishdi"

#: templates/home/index.html:173
msgid ""
"Tashkent International University has been recognized as one of the leading "
"institutions in Central Asia for its outstanding academic programs and "
"research contributions."
