"Toshkent Xalqaro Universiteti Markaziy Osiyodagi yetakchi ta'lim "
"muassasalaridan biri sifatida e'tirof etildi."

#: templates/home/index.html:188
msgid ""
"TIU launches new AI & Machine Learning research lab in partnership with KAIST"
