"TIU KAIST bilan hamkorlikda yangi sun'iy intellekt va mashina o'rganish "
"laboratoriyasini ishga tushirdi"

#: templates/home/index.html:189
msgid ""
"Tashkent International University has opened a state-of-the-art research "
"laboratory dedicated to artificial intelligence and machine learning..."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent Xalqaro Universiteti sun'iy intellekt va mashina o'rganishga "
"bag'ishlangan zamonaviy tadqiqot laboratoriyasini ochdi..."

