#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html:191
msgid "What qualifications do I need to teach at TIU?"
msgstr "TIUda dars berish uchun qanday malaka kerak?"

#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Academic positions typically require a Master's degree at minimum, with a "
"PhD preferred for senior roles. Relevant teaching experience, research "
"publications, and English language proficiency are also essential. Specific "
"requirements vary by position."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Akademik lavozimlar odatda kamida magistrlik darajasini talab qiladi, yuqori "
"lavozimlar uchun PhD afzaldir. Tegishli o'qitish tajribasi, ilmiy nashrlari "
"va ingliz tilini bilish ham zarur. Maxsus talablar lavozimga qarab farq "
"qiladi.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Akademik lavozimlar uchun kamida magistrlik darajasi talab qilinadi, yuqori "
"lavozimlar uchun PhD afzal ko'riladi. Tegishli o'qitish tajribasi, ilmiy "
"nashrlar va ingliz tilini bilish ham muhim. Aniq talablar lavozimga qarab "
"farq qiladi."

#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html
msgid "Do you hire international faculty?"
msgstr "Siz xalqaro professor-o'qituvchilarni yollaysizmi?"

#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html
msgid ""
"Yes, TIU actively recruits international faculty members. We provide visa "
"support, relocation assistance, and competitive compensation packages for "
"international hires. Our diverse faculty represents multiple nationalities."
msgstr ""
"Ha, TIU xalqaro professor-o'qituvchilarni faol ravishda yollaydi. Biz "
"xalqaro xodimlarga viza qo'llab-quvvatlash, ko'chish yordami va "
"raqobatbardosh kompensatsiya paketlarini taqdim etamiz. Bizning xilma-xil "
"professor-o'qituvchilarimiz ko'plab millatlarni ifodalaydi."

#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html:209
msgid "What benefits does TIU offer employees?"
msgstr "TIU xodimlarga qanday imtiyozlar taklif qiladi?"

#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Benefits include competitive salary, health insurance, professional "
"development funding, conference travel support, subsidised meals on campus, "
"and access to university facilities including the library, gym, and research "
"labs."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Imtiyozlarga raqobatbardosh maosh, tibbiy sug'urta, kasbiy rivojlanish "
"moliyalashtirish, konferensiya safarlari qo'llab-quvvatlash, kampusda "
"subsidiyalangan ovqatlanish va kutubxona, sport zali va ilmiy "
"laboratoriyalarni o'z ichiga olgan universitet ob'ektlaridan foydalanish "
"kiradi.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Imtiyozlar: raqobatbardosh ish haqi, tibbiy sug'urta, kasbiy rivojlanish "
"uchun mablag', konferentsiyalarga safar xarajatlari, kampusda arzon "
"ovqatlanish va kutubxona, sport zali va tadqiqot laboratoriyalaridan "
"foydalanish."

#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html:218
msgid "How long does the hiring process take?"
msgstr "Ishga qabul jarayoni qancha vaqt oladi?"

#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html
msgid ""
"The typical process takes 3–6 weeks from application deadline to offer. This "
"includes initial screening, a teaching demonstration or interview, and "
"reference checks. We aim to communicate decisions promptly to all applicants."
msgstr ""
"Odatiy jarayon ariza muddatidan taklifgacha 3–6 haftani oladi. Bu dastlabki "
"tanlov, o'qitish namoyishi yoki suhbat va tavsiyanomalarni tekshirishni o'z "
"ichiga oladi. Biz barcha arizachilarga qarorlarni tezda yetkazishga "
"intilamiz."

#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html:227
msgid "Can I apply if there are no current openings in my field?"
msgstr ""
"Mening sohamda hozirda ochiq lavozim bo'lmasa ham ariza topshirsam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/careers/hiring.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Absolutely. You can send a speculative application to hr@tiu.uz with your CV "
"and cover letter. We keep promising applications on file and will reach out "
"when a suitable position becomes available."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Albatta. Siz hr@tiu.uz manziliga rezyume va motivatsion xatingiz bilan "
"tashabbuskor ariza yuborishingiz mumkin. Biz istiqbolli arizalarni saqlab "
"qo'yamiz va mos lavozim paydo bo'lganda siz bilan bog'lanamiz.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Albatta. CV va motivatsion xatingizni hr@tiu.uz manziliga yuborishingiz "
"mumkin. Biz istiqbolli arizalarni saqlab qo'yamiz va tegishli vakansiya "
"ochilganda siz bilan bog'lanamiz."

