#: templates/pages/programs/by-faculty.html:36
msgid ""
"TIU's academic programmes are delivered through two faculties, each with "
"dedicated departments, experienced faculty, and strong industry connections. "
"Every programme is taught in English and designed to international standards."
msgstr ""
"TIUning akademik dasturlari ikkita fakultet orqali taqdim etiladi, har "
"birida maxsus bo'limlar, tajribali o'qituvchilar va kuchli soha aloqalari "
"mavjud. Har bir dastur ingliz tilida o'qitiladi va xalqaro standartlarga "
"moslashtirilgan."

#: templates/pages/programs/by-faculty.html:37
msgid ""
"Whether you're drawn to law, business, technology, or education, you'll find "
"a programme that matches your ambitions and prepares you for a global career."
msgstr ""
