msgstr "Davlat moliyasi va xalqaro moliya"

msgid "PhD and DCS Programs"
msgstr "PhD va DCs dasturlari"

msgid ""
"Tashkent International University — a modern private university providing "
"world-class education in the heart of Uzbekistan."
msgstr ""
"Tashkent International University — O'zbekiston qalbida jahon darajasidagi "
"ta'lim beruvchi zamonaviy xususiy universitet."

msgid ""
"Join Tashkent International University and step into a world of academic "
"excellence, personal growth, and limitless opportunities."
msgstr ""
"TIUga qo'shiling — akademik mukammallik, shaxsiy o'sish va cheksiz "
"imkoniyatlar dunyosiga qadam qo'ying."

msgid "University"
msgstr "Universitet"

msgid "Modern Campus Life"
msgstr "Zamonaviy kampus muhiti"

msgid ""
"Our modern campus, located on the Small Ring Road in the center of Tashkent, "
"offers everything needed for academic success and personal development. "
"Modern classrooms, healthcare facilities, student clubs, a contemporary "
"dormitory, and a vibrant community are waiting for you. At TIU, you will "
"find the perfect environment for learning, networking, and growth."
msgstr ""
"Toshkentning markazidagi Kichik Halqa Yo'lda joylashgan zamonaviy kampusimiz "
"akademik muvaffaqiyat va shaxsiy rivojlanish uchun zarur bo'lgan hamma "
"narsani taqdim etadi. Zamonaviy sinflar, sog'liqni saqlash inshootlari, "
"talabalar klublari, zamonaviy talabalar yotoqxonasi va jonli hamjamiyat "
"sizni kutmoqda. TIUda siz o'rganish, aloqalarni o'rnatish va taraqqiyot "
"uchun mukammal muhit topasiz."

msgid "International Programs"
msgstr "Xalqaro dasturlar"

msgid "2+2 Program"
msgstr "2+2 programa dasturi"

msgid ""
"Students studying under the 2+2 program at TIU and prestigious international "
"partner universities earn two diplomas. The program provides a wide range of "
"skills, global experience, and competitive advantage in a short period."
msgstr ""
"TIU va nufuzli xorijiy hamkor universitetlarda 2+2 dasturida o'qib, "
"talabalar ikki diplomga ega bo'lishadi. Dastur qisqa vaqt ichida keng "
"ko'nikmalar, global tajriba va raqobatbardosh ustunlik beradi."

msgid ""
"TIU's academic exchange program is organized in partnership with "
"international universities. It allows students to study abroad, gain "
"international experience, and expand their academic and cultural skills."
msgstr ""
"Tashkent International University (TIU) talabalari uchun xalqaro "
"universitetlar bilan hamkorlik asosida tashkil etilgan akademik almashinuv "
"dasturidir. Ushbu dastur talabalarga chet el universitetlarida o'qish, "
"xalqaro tajriba olish va o'z bilim hamda madaniy ko'nikmalarini kengaytirish "
"imkonini beradi."

msgid ""
"TIU students have the opportunity to participate in internships at partner "
"universities and organizations abroad. The program enables students to "
"develop professional, language, and cultural skills while building a global "
"professional network. The university's International Relations Office "
"supports students in finding internship placements and managing all "
"organizational matters."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalari amaliyot (internship) dasturini chetdagi hamkor "
"universitetlar va tashkilotlarda o'tkazish imkoniga ega. Bu dastur orqali "
"talabalar xorijiy ish muhitida kasbiy tajriba, til va madaniy ko'nikmalarni "
"rivojlantirish hamda global professional tarmoq yaratish imkoniyatiga ega "
"bo'ladilar. Universitet Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi talabalarni amaliyot "
"joylarini topishda va barcha tashkilotchilik masalalarida qo'llab-"
"quvvatlaydi."

msgid "Where Knowledge Meets Opportunity"
msgstr "Bilim va imkoniyatlar birlashgan maskan"

msgid ""
"Tashkent International University (TIU) is a modern private university "
"located in Tashkent, established in October 2023. TIU develops partnerships "
"with prestigious international universities and organizations, offering "
"students wide-ranging academic opportunities. Our main goal is to provide "
"students with a solid foundation for success in their chosen careers and "
"life. Start building your future today — join TIU."
msgstr ""
"Tashkent International University (TIU) — Toshkent shahrida joylashgan "
"zamonaviy xususiy universitet bo'lib, 2023-yil oktyabr oyida tashkil "
"etilgan. TIU nufuzli xorijiy universitetlar va tashkilotlar bilan "
"hamkorlikni rivojlantirib, talabalarga keng akademik imkoniyatlar yaratadi. "
"Bizning asosiy maqsadimiz — talabalarimizni tanlagan kasbi va hayot yo'lida "
"muvaffaqiyatga erishishlari uchun mustahkam poydevor bilan ta'minlash. "
"Kelajagingizni bugundan boshlang — TIUga qo'shiling."

msgid "2+2 DUAL DEGREE"
msgstr "2+2 QO'SHMA DIPLOM"

msgid "STUDENT EXCHANGE"
msgstr "TALABA ALMASHUVI"

msgid "Student Exchange Program"
msgstr "Talaba almashuv dasturi"

msgid "INTERNSHIP"
msgstr "AMALIYOT"

msgid "Internship Program"
msgstr "Amaliyot dasturi"

msgid ""
"We aspire to become a renowned institution of higher education by training "
"skilled and knowledgeable professionals who make a positive impact on the "
"world."
msgstr ""
"Biz butun dunyoga ijobiy ta'sir ko'rsatadigan malakali va bilimli "
"mutaxassislarni tayyorlash orqali mashhur oliy o'quv yurti sifatida "
"shakllanishga intilamiz."

msgid "Academic excellence, a culture of innovation, and success for all"
msgstr ""
"Akademik mukammallik, innovatsiya madaniyati va barchaning muvaffaqiyati"

msgid ""
"We achieve our goals through a commitment to academic excellence, a culture "
"of innovation, and the success of our students, faculty, and staff. Our "
"university strives to provide students with high-quality education and "
"professional development, equipping them with the knowledge and skills to "
"become leading specialists in their chosen fields."
msgstr ""
"Biz maqsadlarimizga akademik mukammallikka sodiqlik, innovatsiya madaniyati "
"va talabalarimiz, professor-o'qituvchilarimiz va xodimlarimizning "
"muvaffaqiyati orqali erishamiz. Universitetimiz talabalarga yuqori sifatli "
"ta'lim va malaka oshirish, ularni o'zlari tanlagan yo'nalishlar bo'yicha "
"yetakchi mutaxassis bo'lishi uchun bilim va ko'nikmalar bilan ta'minlashga "
"intiladi."

msgid ""
"We are committed to creating a learning environment that fosters creativity, "
"critical thinking, and lifelong learning."
msgstr ""
"Biz kreativlikni, tanqidiy fikrlashni va uzoq muddatli ta'limni qo'llab-"
"quvvatlovchi o'quv muhitini yaratishga intilamiz."

msgid "Preparing professionals who shape"
msgstr "Kelajakni shakllantiradigan mutaxassislarni"

msgid "the future"
msgstr "tayyorlash"

msgid ""
"Our mission is to train qualified and knowledgeable professionals who make a "
"positive impact on the world. We provide students with a comprehensive "
"education that helps them succeed in their chosen profession and life."
msgstr ""
"Bizning vazifamiz — butun dunyoga ijobiy ta'sir ko'rsatadigan malakali va "
"bilimli mutaxassislarni tayyorlash. Biz talabalarga tanlagan kasbi va "
"hayotida muvaffaqiyatga erishishga yordam beradigan har tomonlama ta'lim "
"beramiz."

msgid ""
"The university values diversity, creativity, and innovation, encouraging "
"students to think critically, communicate effectively, and make a positive "
"contribution to society."
msgstr ""
"Universitet xilma-xillik, kreativlik va innovatsiyalarni qadrlaydi, "
"talabalarni tanqidiy fikrlash, samarali muloqot qilish va jamiyatga ijobiy "
"ta'sir ko'rsatishga undaydi."

msgid "Research, innovation, and"
msgstr "Tadqiqot, innovatsiya va"

msgid "global partnerships"
msgstr "global hamkorlik"

msgid ""
"TIU places great emphasis on research and innovation, encouraging students "
"to engage in research activities and collaborate with industry centers. TIU "
"strives to establish partnerships with universities and organizations around "
"the world, offering students opportunities to study abroad and gain valuable "
"international experience."
msgstr ""
"TIU tadqiqot va innovatsiyalarga katta e'tibor qaratadi va talabalarni "
"tadqiqot faoliyati bilan shug'ullanishga hamda sanoat markazlari bilan "
"hamkorlik qilishga undaydi. TIU dunyoning ko'plab universitetlari va "
"tashkilotlari bilan hamkorlik aloqalarini o'rnatishga intiladi, talabalarga "
"chet elda ta'lim olish va foydali xalqaro tajriba orttirish imkoniyatlarini "
"taqdim etadi."

msgid ""
"Tashkent International University is committed to providing students with a "
"comprehensive education that helps them succeed in their chosen careers and "
"in life. The university values diversity, creativity, and innovation, "
"encouraging students to think critically, communicate effectively, and make "
"a positive impact on society."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universiteti talabalarga ularni tanlagan kasbi va hayotida "
"muvaffaqiyatga erishishga yordam beradigan har tomonlama ta'lim berish "
"majburiyatini oladi. Universitet xilma-xillik, kreativlik va "
"innovatsiyalarni qadrlaydi, talabalarni tanqidiy fikrlash, samarali muloqot "
"qilish va jamiyatga ijobiy ta'sir ko'rsatishga undaydi."

msgid ""
"We uphold the highest standards of teaching and learning, ensuring our "
"students receive an education that meets international benchmarks."
msgstr ""
"Biz o'qitish va o'rganishning eng yuqori standartlarini ushlab turamiz, "
"talabalarimiz xalqaro mezonlarga javob beradigan ta'lim olishini "
"ta'minlaymiz."

msgid "High-quality curricula aligned with global educational standards"
msgstr "Global ta'lim standartlariga mos yuqori sifatli o'quv dasturlari"

msgid "Experienced international and local faculty"
msgstr "Tajribali xalqaro va mahalliy professor-o'qituvchilar"

msgid "Continuous improvement of teaching methods and academic programs"
msgstr "O'qitish usullari va akademik dasturlarni doimiy takomillashtirish"

msgid "Innovation and"
msgstr "Innovatsiya va"

