"We foster a culture where new ideas thrive, encouraging students and faculty "
"to push boundaries and contribute to the advancement of knowledge."
msgstr ""
"Biz yangi g'oyalar rivojlanadigan madaniyatni shakllantiramiz, talabalar va "
"professor-o'qituvchilarni chegaralarni kengaytirishga va bilim rivojiga "
"hissa qo'shishga undaymiz."

msgid "Student involvement in research projects from the early stages of study"
msgstr ""
"Talabalarni o'qishning dastlabki bosqichlaridan tadqiqot loyihalariga jalb "
"qilish"

msgid "Partnerships with industry and research institutions"
msgstr "Sanoat va tadqiqot muassasalari bilan hamkorlik"

msgid "Supporting creative thinking and entrepreneurial initiatives"
msgstr "Ijodiy fikrlash va tadbirkorlik tashabbuslarini qo'llab-quvvatlash"

msgid "Global"
msgstr "Global"

msgid "Engagement"
msgstr "hamkorlik"

msgid ""
"We are building bridges across borders, creating opportunities for our "
"students to gain international experience and develop a global perspective."
msgstr ""
"Biz chegaralar aro ko'priklar qurib, talabalarimizga xalqaro tajriba "
"orttirish va global nuqtai nazarni rivojlantirish imkoniyatlarini "
