msgid ""
"We don't just exist to teach. We're here to help you prepare for life after "
"university. Whether that's a year studying abroad, a rewarding work "
"placement, or a volunteering role you can't get anywhere else. Learn how to "
"get career-ready at an Open Day."
msgstr ""
"Biz faqat dars berish uchun emasmiz. Universitetdan keyingi hayotga "
"tayyorlanishingizga yordam beramiz — xorijda o'qish, foydali amaliyot yoki "
"boshqa joyda topa olmaydigan ko'ngillilik tajribasi bo'lsin. Ochiq eshiklar "
"kunida karyerangizga qanday tayyorlanishni bilib oling."

