msgstr ""
"TIU va hamkor universitetdan diplomlar oling — O'zbekistonda va xalqaro "
"miqyosda to'liq tan olingan."

msgid "Why choose a joint degree?"
msgstr "Nima uchun qo'shma diplomni tanlash kerak?"

msgid "Competitive Advantage"
msgstr "Raqobatbardosh ustunlik"

msgid ""
"Holders of two degrees stand out in front of employers, expanding career "
"opportunities across multiple fields and industries."
msgstr ""
"Ikki diplomga ega bo'lganlar ish beruvchilar oldida ajralib turadi va turli "
"sohalarda karyera imkoniyatlarini kengaytiradi."

msgid "Global Experience"
msgstr "Xalqaro tajriba"

msgid ""
"Living and studying in another country develops your international "
"perspective, cross-cultural skills, and professional network."
msgstr ""
"Boshqa mamlakatda yashash va o'qish xalqaro dunyoqarash, madaniyatlararo "
"ko'nikmalar va professional aloqalarni rivojlantiradi."

msgid "Personal Growth"
msgstr "Shaxsiy o'sish"

msgid ""
"The program fosters independence, problem-solving skills, and adaptability — "
"qualities that prepare you for success in today's fast-changing world."
msgstr ""
"Dastur mustaqillik, muammolarni hal qilish ko'nikmalari va "
"moslashuvchanlikni rivojlantiradi — bugungi tez o'zgarayotgan dunyoda "
"muvaffaqiyatga tayyorlaydigan sifatlar."

msgid "Fast Track"
msgstr "Tez yo'l"

msgid ""
"Earn two bachelor's degrees in a shorter time compared to completing each "
"program separately, allowing you to enter the job market sooner."
msgstr ""
"Har bir dasturni alohida tugatishga nisbatan qisqa vaqtda ikkita bakalavriat "
"darajasini oling va mehnat bozoriga tezroq kiring."

msgid "Important Information"
msgstr "Muhim ma'lumot"

msgid "Fees and scholarships"
msgstr "To'lov va stipendiyalar"

msgid ""
"Students participating in the 2+2 program are not required to pay any fees "
"to TIU after transferring to the partner university. Any scholarships held "
"at TIU before the transfer are considered cancelled."
msgstr ""
"2+2 dasturida ishtirok etayotgan talabalar hamkor universitetga o'tgandan "
"keyin TIU ga hech qanday to'lov to'lashi shart emas. O'tishdan oldin TIU "
"dagi stipendiyalar bekor qilingan hisoblanadi."

msgid ""
"However, in some cases, agreements between TIU and the receiving university "
"may require students to continue paying TIU fees. Students are advised to "
"consult with the International Relations Department regarding payment terms "
"and scholarships before applying."
msgstr ""
"Biroq ba'zi hollarda TIU va qabul qiluvchi universitet o'rtasidagi kelishuv "
"talabalardan TIU ga to'lovni davom ettirishni talab qilishi mumkin. "
"Talabalarga ariza topshirishdan oldin to'lov shartlari va stipendiyalar "
"haqida Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi bilan maslahatlashish tavsiya etiladi."

msgid "Contact International Relations"
msgstr "Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qiling"

msgid ""
"Study at an international partner university for a semester or academic year "
"— expand your horizons without extending your studies."
msgstr ""
"Xalqaro hamkor universitetda bir semestr yoki o'quv yili davomida ta'lim "
"oling — o'qish muddatini uzaytirmasdan ko'lamingizni kengaytiring."

msgid "Discover the world"
msgstr "Dunyoni kashf eting"

msgid "while you study."
msgstr "o'qish davomida."

msgid ""
"TIU's academic exchange program is organized in partnership with "
"international universities. It gives students the opportunity to study "
"abroad, gain international experience, and broaden their academic and "
"cultural skills — all while remaining enrolled at TIU."
msgstr ""
"TIU ning akademik almashinuv dasturi xalqaro universitetlar bilan "
"hamkorlikda tashkil etilgan. U talabalarga xorijda ta'lim olish, xalqaro "
"tajriba orttirish va akademik hamda madaniy ko'nikmalarini kengaytirish "
"imkonini beradi — barchasi TIU da ro'yxatda qolgan holda."

msgid ""
"Exchange students immerse themselves in a different academic environment, "
"improve their language abilities, and develop the independence and "
"adaptability that employers highly value. Credits earned at the partner "
"university transfer directly back to your TIU degree."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv talabalari boshqa akademik muhitga singishadi, til bilimlarini "
"oshiradi va ish beruvchilar yuqori baholaydigan mustaqillik va "
"moslashuvchanlikni rivojlantiradi. Hamkor universitetda to'plangan kreditlar "
"TIU diplomingizga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'tkaziladi."

msgid ""
"The International Relations Department supports you at every step — from "
"choosing a destination and preparing documents to arranging accommodation "
"and visa support."
msgstr ""
"Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi har bir qadamda sizni qo'llab-quvvatlaydi — manzil "
"tanlashdan hujjatlar tayyorlash, turar joy va viza yordamigacha."

msgid "Want two full degrees instead?"
msgstr "Ikkita to'liq diplom olishni xohlaysizmi?"

msgid ""
"If you're looking to graduate with diplomas from two universities, explore "
"our Joint Degrees program."
msgstr ""
"Ikkita universitetdan diplom bilan bitirmoqchi bo'lsangiz, Qo'shma diplom "
"dasturimizni ko'ring."

msgid "What you gain"
msgstr "Nimaga ega bo'lasiz"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An exchange at TIU is more than studying abroad — it's a complete "
"international experience."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"TIU dagi almashinuv dasturi xorijda o'qishdan ko'proq narsa — bu to'liq "
"xalqaro tajriba.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"TIUda almashinuv — chet elda o'qishdan ko'proq narsa, bu to'laqonli xalqaro "
"tajriba."

msgid "Seamless Credit Transfer"
msgstr "Muammosiz kredit transferi"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All credits earned at the partner university transfer directly to your TIU "
"degree. No repeated courses, no time lost."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Hamkor universitetda to'plangan barcha kreditlar TIU diplomingizga "
"to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'tkaziladi. Takroriy kurslar yo'q, vaqt yo'qotilmaydi.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Hamkor universitetda to'plangan barcha kreditlar bevosita TIU diplomingizga "
"o'tkaziladi. Takroriy fanlar yo'q, vaqt yo'qotilmaydi."

msgid "No Extra Tuition"
msgstr "Qo'shimcha to'lovsiz"

msgid ""
"You continue paying TIU fees during your exchange. Partner university "
"tuition is waived under our agreements."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv davomida TIU to'lovini to'lashda davom etasiz. Hamkor universitet "
"to'lovi kelishuvlarimiz asosida bekor qilinadi."

msgid "Cultural Immersion"
msgstr "Madaniy tajriba"

msgid ""
"Live in a new country, experience a different academic culture first-hand, "
"and develop cross-cultural skills valued by employers worldwide."
msgstr ""
"Yangi mamlakatda yashang, boshqa akademik madaniyatni bevosita his qiling va "
"dunyo bo'ylab ish beruvchilar qadrlaydigan madaniyatlararo ko'nikmalarni "
"rivojlantiring."

msgid "International Network"
msgstr "Xalqaro aloqalar"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Build lasting friendships and professional connections with students from "
"around the world."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Dunyo bo'ylab talabalar bilan uzoq muddatli do'stlik va professional "
"aloqalar o'rnating.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Dunyo bo'ylab talabalar bilan uzoq muddatli do'stlik va kasbiy aloqalar "
"o'rnating."

msgid "Full Support"
msgstr "To'liq qo'llab-quvvatlash"

msgid ""
"The International Relations Department helps with visa applications, "
"accommodation, travel logistics, and pre-departure orientation."
msgstr ""
"Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi viza arizalari, turar joy, sayohat logistikasi va "
"jo'nashdan oldingi yo'l-yo'riq bilan yordam beradi."

msgid "Career Advantage"
msgstr "Karyera ustunligi"

msgid ""
"International experience on your CV makes you stand out. Exchange alumni "
"consistently report stronger career outcomes after graduation."
msgstr ""
"Rezyumedagi xalqaro tajriba sizni ajratib turadi. Almashinuv bitiruvchilari "
"bitirganidan keyin kuchli karyera natijalarini ko'rsatadi."

msgid "How to apply"
msgstr "Qanday ariza topshirish"

msgid "Follow these steps to start your exchange journey."
msgstr "Almashinuv sayohatingizni boshlash uchun quyidagi qadamlarni bajaring."

msgid "Choose a destination"
msgstr "Manzilni tanlang"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Browse available partner universities and select the one that matches your "
"academic interests and goals."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Mavjud hamkor universitetlarni ko'rib chiqing va akademik qiziqishlari va "
"maqsadlaringizga mos keluvchisini tanlang.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Mavjud hamkor universitetlarni ko'rib chiqing va akademik qiziqishlaringiz "
"va maqsadlaringizga mosini tanlang."

msgid "Submit your application"
msgstr "Arizangizni topshiring"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Apply through the International Relations Department with your transcript, "
"motivation letter, and language certificate."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi orqali transkript, motivatsiya xati va til "
"sertifikatingiz bilan ariza topshiring.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Transkript, motivatsion xat va til sertifikatingiz bilan Xalqaro aloqalar "
"bo'limi orqali ariza topshiring."

msgid "Get approved"
msgstr "Tasdiqlang"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"After review by TIU and the partner university, you'll receive your "
"acceptance and start preparing for departure."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"TIU va hamkor universitet ko'rib chiqqandan so'ng qabul xatingizni olasiz va "
"jo'nashga tayyorlanishni boshlaysiz.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"TIU va hamkor universitet arizangizni ko'rib chiqqach, qabul xatini olasiz "
"va jo'nash uchun tayyorgarlik boshlaysiz."

msgid "Study abroad"
msgstr "Xorijda o'qing"

msgid ""
"Spend one or two semesters at the partner university. Your credits transfer "
"back to TIU upon your return."
msgstr ""
"Hamkor universitetda bir yoki ikki semestr o'tkazing. Qaytganingizda "
"kreditlaringiz TIU ga o'tkaziladi."

msgid "Fees during exchange"
msgstr "Almashinuv davridagi to'lovlar"

msgid ""
"During your exchange semester, you continue paying your regular TIU tuition. "
"Partner university tuition fees are waived under our bilateral agreements. "
"However, students are responsible for their own travel, accommodation, and "
"living expenses abroad."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv semestri davomida odatiy TIU to'lovini to'lashda davom etasiz. "
"Hamkor universitet to'lovlari ikki tomonlama kelishuvlar asosida bekor "
"qilinadi. Biroq talabalar xorijdagi sayohat, turar joy va yashash "
"xarajatlari uchun o'zlari javobgar."

msgid ""
"Students are advised to consult with the International Relations Department "
"for detailed information about costs and available financial support before "
"applying."
msgstr ""
"Talabalarga ariza topshirishdan oldin xarajatlar va mavjud moliyaviy yordam "
"haqida batafsil ma'lumot uchun Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qilish "
"tavsiya etiladi."

