#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"Head to our application portal to begin the process. Make sure you have your "
"documents ready and apply before the deadline for your chosen programme."
msgstr ""
"Ariza topshirish portaliga o'ting. Hujjatlaringizni tayyorlab, tanlagan "
"dasturingiz uchun belgilangan muddatgacha ariza topshiring."

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "Start your application"
msgstr "Ariza topshirish"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "What happens if I miss the application deadline?"
msgstr "Ariza topshirish muddatini o'tkazib yuborsam nima bo'ladi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"If you miss the deadline for your chosen intake, you may still be considered "
"for late admission depending on programme availability. Contact the "
"Admissions Office at admissions@tiu.uz to discuss your options. We recommend "
"applying as early as possible to secure your place."
msgstr ""
"Tanlagan qabul davringiz muddatini o'tkazib yuborsangiz, dasturda joy "
"mavjudligiga qarab kechikkan qabul uchun ko'rib chiqilishingiz mumkin. "
"Imkoniyatlaringizni muhokama qilish uchun Qabul bo'limiga admissions@tiu.uz "
"orqali murojaat qiling. O'rningizni ta'minlash uchun iloji boricha erta "
"ariza topshirishni tavsiya etamiz."

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "When does the academic year start and end?"
msgstr "O'quv yili qachon boshlanadi va tugaydi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"The academic year begins in September with Orientation Week and runs through "
"to June the following year. Semester 1 covers September to January, Semester "
"2 runs from February to May, and the summer period (June-August) includes "
"graduation ceremonies and resit examinations."
msgstr ""
"O'quv yili sentabrda Tanishuv haftasi bilan boshlanadi va keyingi yilning "
"iyunigacha davom etadi. 1-semestr sentabrdan yanvargacha, 2-semestr "
"fevraldan maygacha bo'lib, yozgi davr (iyun-avgust) bitiruv marosimlari va "
"qayta topshirish imtihonlarini o'z ichiga oladi."

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "Are there different deadlines for international students?"
msgstr "Xorijiy talabalar uchun boshqa muddatlar belgilanganmi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"Yes. International applicants typically have an earlier deadline to allow "
"time for visa processing, document verification, and travel arrangements. "
"Check the Application Deadlines table above for the specific dates that "
"apply to your category."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Xorijiy abituriyentlar uchun viza rasmiylashtirish, hujjatlarni "
"tekshirish va sayohat tayyorgarligiga vaqt ajratish maqsadida muddatlar "
"odatda ertaroq belgilanadi. Sizning toifangizga tegishli aniq sanalarni "
"yuqoridagi Qabul muddatlari jadvalidan tekshiring."

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid "How long does it take to receive a decision after applying?"
msgstr "Ariza topshirgandan keyin javob olish qancha vaqt oladi?"

#: templates/pages/admissions/deadlines.html
msgid ""
"Most applicants receive a decision within 2-4 weeks of submitting a complete "
"application. During peak periods, it may take slightly longer. You can track "
"your application status through the student portal or by contacting "
"admissions@tiu.uz."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pchilik abituriyentlar to'liq ariza topshirgandan so'ng 2-4 hafta ichida "
"javob oladi. Yuqori talabli davrlarda bu biroz ko'proq vaqt olishi mumkin. "
"Ariza holatini talabalar portali orqali yoki admissions@tiu.uz ga murojaat "
"qilib kuzatishingiz mumkin."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Admission Process - International Students | TIU"
msgstr "Qabul jarayoni - Xorijiy talabalar | TIU"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Your step-by-step guide to joining TIU as an international student — from "
"application to arrival."
msgstr ""
"TIU da xorijiy talaba sifatida o'qishni boshlash yo'lingiz — ariza "
"topshirishdan kelguncha."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Applying to TIU is simple and straightforward"
msgstr "TIU ga ariza topshirish oson va tushunarli"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Whether you're applying from Kazakhstan, South Korea, Turkey, or anywhere "
"else in the world — the process is the same. Everything can be completed "
"online, there's no application fee, and our International Office is "
"available to assist you at every stage. Most applicants receive a decision "
"within two weeks."
msgstr ""
"Qozog'istondan, Janubiy Koreyadan, Turkiyadan yoki dunyoning boshqa "
"burchagidan ariza topshirayotganingizdan qat'i nazar — jarayon bir xil. "
"Hamma narsani onlayn bajarish mumkin, ariza topshirish bepul va Xalqaro "
"ishlar bo'limimiz har bir bosqichda sizga yordam berishga tayyor. Ko'pchilik "
"abituriyentlar ikki hafta ichida javob oladi."

