"documents online completely free of charge."
msgstr ""
"Xorijiy talabalar ariza topshirish uchun hech qanday to'lov to'lamaydi. "
"Ariza va hujjatlaringizni onlayn tarzda mutlaqo bepul yuboring."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
