"Onlayn shaklni to'ldiring va hujjatlaringizni yuklang: pasport, "
"transkriptlar, ingliz tili sertifikati va motivatsion xat"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Receive your offer"
msgstr "Taklif xatingizni oling"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Get your admission decision within 2 weeks. Accept the offer and pay the "
"tuition deposit to confirm your place"
msgstr ""
"2 hafta ichida qabul natijasini oling. Taklifni qabul qilib, o'rningizni "
"band qilish uchun dastlabki to'lovni amalga oshiring"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Visa & arrival"
msgstr "Viza va kelish"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Receive your invitation letter, apply for your student visa, and prepare for "
"your journey to Tashkent"
msgstr ""
"Taklifnomangizni oling, talaba vizasiga ariza topshiring va Toshkentga "
"sayohatingizga tayyorlaning"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Prepare the following before starting your application. All documents should "
"be in English, or accompanied by a certified translation."
msgstr ""
"Ariza topshirishdan oldin quyidagilarni tayyorlab qo'ying. Barcha hujjatlar "
"ingliz tilida yoki tasdiqlangan tarjimasi bilan bo'lishi kerak."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A personal statement explaining why you want to study at TIU and your career "
"goals"
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"TIU da nima uchun o'qishni xohlayotganingiz va karyera maqsadlaringiz haqida "
"shaxsiy xat\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"TIUda nima uchun o'qishni xohlayotganingiz va karera maqsadlaringizni "
"tushuntiruvchi shaxsiy bayonot"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Accommodation & arrival support"
msgstr "Turar joy va kelish bo'yicha yordam"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "International students arriving at TIU"
msgstr "TIU ga kelayotgan xorijiy talabalar"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Don't leave it too late. International applicants have an earlier deadline "
"to allow time for visa processing, document verification, and travel "
"arrangements. Apply early to secure your place and accommodation."
msgstr ""
"Oxirgi kunga qoldirmang. Xorijiy abituriyentlar uchun viza rasmiyatlari, "
"hujjatlarni tekshirish va sayohat tashkil etishga vaqt ajratish maqsadida "
"muddat ertaroq belgilangan. O'rningiz va turar joyingizni band qilish uchun "
"vaqtida ariza topshiring."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Can I apply without an IELTS or TOEFL score?"
msgstr "IELTS yoki TOEFL natijasisiz ariza topshirsa bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"If you completed your secondary or university education in English, you may "
"be exempt from the language test requirement. Contact our admissions team "
"with your academic documents and we'll confirm your eligibility."
msgstr ""
"Agar o'rta yoki oliy ta'limni ingliz tilida olgan bo'lsangiz, til imtihoni "
"talabidan ozod bo'lishingiz mumkin. Ta'lim hujjatlaringiz bilan qabul "
"bo'limimizga murojaat qiling — muvofiqligingizni tasdiqlaymiz."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "How long does the visa process take?"
msgstr "Viza rasmiyatlari qancha vaqt oladi?"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Once you receive your invitation letter from TIU, the student visa is "
"typically processed within 5–10 working days at your local Uzbek embassy or "
"consulate. We recommend applying for your visa at least 4–6 weeks before the "
"semester starts."
msgstr ""
"TIU dan taklifnoma olganingizdan so'ng, talaba vizasi odatda mahalliy "
"O'zbekiston elchixonasi yoki konsulligida 5–10 ish kuni ichida "
"rasmiylashtriladi. Vizaga kamida semestr boshlanishidan 4–6 hafta oldin "
"ariza topshirishni tavsiya etamiz."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Yes. TIU offers student housing options near campus. International students "
"are given priority for university accommodation. We can also help you find "
"private rental options in Tashkent at affordable rates starting from $200/"
"month."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU kampus yaqinida talabalar uchun turar joy imkoniyatlarini taqdim "
"etadi. Xorijiy talabalarga universitet turar joyida ustunlik beriladi. "
"Shuningdek, Toshkentda oyiga 200 dollardan boshlanadigan qulay narxlarda "
"shaxsiy ijaraga uy topishda ham yordam beramiz."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Yes. TIU offers merit-based scholarships covering up to 50% of tuition for "
"high-achieving international applicants. All applicants are automatically "
"considered — no separate scholarship application is needed."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU yuqori natijalarga erishgan xorijiy abituriyentlarga o'quv "
"to'lovining 50% gacha qoplaydigan grantlar taqdim etadi. Barcha "
"abituriyentlar avtomatik ravishda ko'rib chiqiladi — alohida grant arizasi "
"talab etilmaydi."

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid "Can I transfer credits from another university?"
msgstr "Boshqa universitetdan kreditlarni o'tkazsa bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/international/admission-process.html
msgid ""
"Credit transfer is evaluated on a case-by-case basis. Submit your previous "
"university transcripts along with course descriptions, and our academic "
"office will assess which credits can be transferred to your TIU programme."
msgstr ""
"Kredit o'tkazish har bir holat uchun alohida ko'rib chiqiladi. Oldingi "
"universitetingiz transkripti va fan tavsiflari bilan birga topshiring — "
"akademik bo'limimiz qaysi kreditlarni TIU dasturingizga o'tkazish "
"mumkinligini baholaydi."

msgid "Visa Support for International Students"
msgstr "Xorijiy talabalar uchun viza yordami"

msgid ""
"Tashkent International University welcomes international students and "
"provides guidance during the visa and arrival process."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent Xalqaro Universiteti xorijiy talabalarni qabul qiladi va viza olish "
"hamda kelish jarayonida yo'l-yo'riq ko'rsatadi."

msgid "We can support you with:"
msgstr "Biz sizga quyidagilarda yordam bera olamiz:"

msgid "Admission-related documents"
msgstr "Qabul uchun kerakli hujjatlar"

msgid "Invitation and visa guidance"
msgstr "Taklifnoma va viza bo'yicha maslahat"

msgid "Arrival information"
msgstr "Kelish haqida ma'lumot"

msgid "Registration support"
msgstr "Ro'yxatdan o'tishda yordam"

msgid "Communication with the International Relations Department"
msgstr "Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi bilan bog'lanish"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Applicants are encouraged to check current visa requirements through the "
"official consular authorities of Uzbekistan."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Abituriyentlarga O'zbekistonning rasmiy konsullik organlari orqali joriy "
"viza talablarini tekshirish tavsiya etiladi.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Ariza beruvchilarga O'zbekistonning rasmiy konsullik idoralari orqali joriy "
"viza talablarini tekshirish tavsiya etiladi."

msgid ""
"For more information, please contact the International Relations Department"
msgstr "Batafsil ma'lumot uchun Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qiling"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"Find your home in Tashkent — from university housing to private rentals, "
"we'll help you settle in."
msgstr ""
"Toshkentda o'z uyingizni toping — universitet yotoqxonasidan tortib xususiy "
"ijaraga qadar, joylashishingizga yordam beramiz."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Home sweet <em>Tashkent</em>"
msgstr "Qadrdon <em>Toshkent</em>"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"This isn't just a place to stay — it's where your university journey begins. "
"The late-night study sessions, the friendships that last a lifetime, the "
"moments that shape who you'll become. Living near campus puts you right at "
"the heart of it all, just minutes from lectures, the library, and student "
"life."
msgstr ""
"Bu shunchaki yashash joyi emas — bu universitet hayotingiz boshlanadigan "
"maskanning o'zi. Kechki soatlardan tongga qadar davom etgan darslar, umrbod "
"do'stliklar, sizni shakllantiradigan lahzalar. Kampus yaqinida yashash sizni "
"barcha voqealar markaziga olib qo'yadi — ma'ruzalar, kutubxona va talabalar "
"hayotiga bir necha daqiqa yaqin."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Your room: guaranteed"
msgstr "Xonangiz: kafolatlangan"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"International students accepted to TIU are guaranteed accommodation support. "
"Apply by <strong>1 August</strong> in your year of entry to secure your "
"place in university-arranged housing."
msgstr ""
"TIU ga qabul qilingan xalqaro talabalar turar joy bilan ta'minlanadi. "
"Universitet tomonidan tashkil etilgan turar joyda o'rningizni band qilish "
"uchun o'qishga kirgan yilingizda <strong>1 avgustgacha</strong> ariza "
"topshiring."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"Whether you're looking for a shared student apartment or a private studio, "
"TIU's International Office will help you find the right option. Rent in "
"Tashkent starts from just $200/month — making it one of the most affordable "
"student cities in Asia."
msgstr ""
"Sherikli talabalar kvartirasi yoki shaxsiy studiya izlayapsizmi — TIU "
"Xalqaro bo'limi sizga eng mos variantni topishda yordam beradi. Toshkentda "
"ijara narxi atigi $200/oydan boshlanadi — bu Osiyodagi eng arzon talabalar "
"shaharlaridan biri."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Enquire about housing"
msgstr "Turar joy haqida so'rov yuborish"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Student accommodation in Tashkent"
msgstr "Toshkentda talabalar turar joyi"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "University Student Residence"
msgstr "Universitet talabalar yotoqxonasi"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "FROM $200 P/M"
msgstr "$200/OYDAN BOSHLAB"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "10 OR 12 MONTHS"
msgstr "10 YOKI 12 OY"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Affordable, social, convenient"
msgstr "Arzon, do'stona, qulay"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"TIU's partner student residence is the most popular choice for international "
"students. Located just 10 minutes from campus, it offers fully furnished "
"shared rooms, communal kitchens, laundry facilities, and 24/7 security. It's "
"where most friendships start — and where you'll feel at home from day one."
msgstr ""
"TIU hamkor talabalar yotoqxonasi xalqaro talabalar orasida eng mashhur "
"tanlovdir. Kampusdan atigi 10 daqiqa masofada joylashgan bo'lib, to'liq "
"jihozlangan umumiy xonalar, oshxona, kir yuvish xizmati va kunlik qo'riqlash "
"xizmatini taklif etadi. Ko'pchilik do'stliklar shu yerda boshlanadi — va "
"birinchi kundan o'zingizni uyingizdek his qilasiz."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Find out more about the residence"
msgstr "Yotoqxona haqida batafsil"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Private Studio Apartments"
msgstr "Shaxsiy studiya kvartiralari"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "FROM $350 P/M"
msgstr "$350/OYDAN BOSHLAB"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "6 OR 12 MONTHS"
msgstr "6 YOKI 12 OY"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Independence and privacy"
msgstr "Mustaqillik va shaxsiy makon"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"For students who prefer their own space, TIU's International Office can help "
"you find a private studio apartment near campus. These come fully furnished "
"with a kitchen, bathroom, Wi-Fi, and air conditioning. Ideal for "
"postgraduate students or those who value a quieter environment for focused "
"study."
msgstr ""
"O'z shaxsiy makonini afzal ko'ruvchi talabalar uchun TIU Xalqaro bo'limi "
"kampus yaqinida shaxsiy studiya kvartira topishda yordam beradi. Ular "
"oshxona, hammom, Wi-Fi va konditsioner bilan to'liq jihozlangan. "
"Magistratura talabalari yoki tinch muhitda o'qishni xohlovchilar uchun ideal "
"tanlov."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Explore private apartments"
msgstr "Shaxsiy kvartiralrni ko'rish"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Shared Student Flats"
msgstr "Sherikli talabalar kvartiralari"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "FROM $150 P/M"
msgstr "$150/OYDAN BOSHLAB"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Budget-friendly, community living"
msgstr "Tejamkor, jamoaviy yashash"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"Share a flat with fellow international or local students in the "
"neighbourhoods around campus. Each student gets their own bedroom, with "
"shared living room, kitchen, and bathroom. It's the most affordable option "
"and a great way to experience Tashkent life while building lasting "
"friendships."
msgstr ""
"Kampus atrofidagi mahallalarda xalqaro yoki mahalliy talabalar bilan "
"birgalikda kvartira ijaralang. Har bir talaba o'z yotoq xonasiga ega, "
"mehmonxona, oshxona va hammom umumiy. Bu eng arzon variant bo'lib, Toshkent "
"hayotini his qilish va mustahkam do'stlik o'rnatishning ajoyib usuli."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Learn about shared flats"
msgstr "Sherikli kvartiralar haqida"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Shared Student Flat"
msgstr "Sherikli talabalar kvartirasi"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Our accommodation guarantee"
msgstr "Turar joy kafolatimiz"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All new international students accepted to TIU are guaranteed accommodation "
"support through our International Office. Just as long as you apply by "
"<strong>1 August</strong> in your year of entry."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"TIU ga qabul qilingan barcha yangi xalqaro talabalar Xalqaro bo'limimiz "
"orqali turar joy bilan ta'minlanadi. Faqat o'qishga kirgan yilingizda "
"<strong>1 avgustgacha</strong> ariza topshinrg kerak.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"TIUga qabul qilingan barcha yangi xalqaro talabalarga Xalqaro ofisimiz "
"orqali turar joy bilan ta'minlanishi kafolatlanadi. Buning uchun kirish "
"yilingizda <strong>1 avgustgacha</strong> ariza topshirishingiz kifoya."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"Whether you need help finding a student residence, a private apartment, or a "
"shared flat — our team will guide you through every step, from booking to "
"move-in day. Contact the <span>International Office</span> to get started."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar yotoqxonasi, shaxsiy kvartira yoki sherikli kvartira topishda "
"yordam kerakmi — jamoamiz band qilishdan ko'chib kirishgacha har bir qadamda "
"sizga yo'l ko'rsatadi. Boshlash uchun <span>Xalqaro bo'lim</span>ga murojaat "
"qiling."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Accommodation FAQs"
msgstr "Turar joy bo'yicha savol-javoblar"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Is accommodation guaranteed for international students?"
msgstr "Xalqaro talabalar uchun turar joy kafolatlanadimi?"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"Yes. All international students accepted to TIU receive accommodation "
"support from the International Office. Apply by 1 August in your year of "
"entry to secure your preferred housing option."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU ga qabul qilingan barcha xalqaro talabalar Xalqaro bo'limdan turar "
"joy bo'yicha yordam oladi. O'zingizga yoqqan turar joy variantini band "
"qilish uchun o'qishga kirgan yilingizda 1 avgustgacha ariza topshiring."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "How much does accommodation cost?"
msgstr "Turar joy narxi qancha?"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"Prices vary depending on the type of housing. Shared student flats start "
"from $150/month, the university student residence from $200/month, and "
"private studio apartments from $350/month. All prices include utilities and "
"basic furnishings."
msgstr ""
"Narxlar turar joy turiga qarab farq qiladi. Sherikli talabalar kvartiralari "
"$150/oydan, universitet yotoqxonasi $200/oydan, shaxsiy studiya kvartiralari "
"$350/oydan boshlanadi. Barcha narxlarga kommunal xizmatlar va asosiy "
"jihozlar kiradi."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Can I choose who I live with?"
msgstr "Kim bilan yashashimni o'zim tanlasam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"Yes. If you and another student both request to share, we'll do our best to "
"accommodate that. Otherwise, we'll match you with a compatible roommate "
"based on your preferences (gender, study habits, language)."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Agar siz va boshqa talaba birga yashashni xohlasangiz, buni amalga "
"oshirishga harakat qilamiz. Aks holda, sizning xohishlaringiz (jins, o'qish "
"tartibi, til) asosida mos sherik topib beramiz."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "What is included in the accommodation?"
msgstr "Turar joyga nimalar kiradi?"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All housing options come fully furnished with a bed, desk, wardrobe, and "
"kitchen access. Wi-Fi, water, and electricity are included. Some options "
"also include air conditioning, laundry facilities, and 24/7 security."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Barcha turar joy variantlari karavot, stol, shkaf va oshxonadan foydalanish "
"imkoniyati bilan to'liq jihozlangan. Wi-Fi, suv va elektr energiyasi "
"kiritilgan. Ba'zi variantlarga konditsioner, kir yuvish xizmati va kunlik "
"qo'riqlash ham kiradi.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Barcha turar joy variantlari karavot, stol, shkaf va oshxonadan foydalanish "
"imkoniyati bilan jihozlangan. Wi-Fi, suv va elektr energiya kiritilgan. "
"Ba'zi variantlarda konditsioner, kir yuvish xonasi va kunlik qo'riqlash ham "
"mavjud."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "Can I move in before the semester starts?"
msgstr "Semestr boshlanishidan oldin ko'chib kirsam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"Yes. International students can typically move in 3–5 days before "
"orientation week begins. The International Office will confirm your exact "
"move-in date once your housing is arranged."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Xalqaro talabalar odatda tanishuv haftasi boshlanishidan 3-5 kun oldin "
"ko'chib kirishi mumkin. Turar joyingiz tayyor bo'lgach, Xalqaro bo'lim aniq "
"ko'chib kirish sanangizni tasdiqlaydi."

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid "What if I need to change my accommodation?"
msgstr "Agar turar joyimni almashtirishim kerak bo'lsa-chi?"

#: templates/pages/international/accommodation.html
msgid ""
"If you're unhappy with your housing, contact the International Office. Room "
"changes are possible within the first 2 weeks of the semester, subject to "
"availability. We'll work with you to find a better fit."
msgstr ""
"Agar turar joyingizdan mamnun bo'lmasangiz, Xalqaro bo'limga murojaat "
"qiling. Semestrning birinchi 2 haftasida, joy mavjudligiga qarab, xona "
"almashtirilishi mumkin. Sizga mosroq variant topishga yordam beramiz."

msgid "Our Global Network"
msgstr "Xalqaro hamkorlik tarmog'imiz"

msgid ""
"TIU collaborates with 40+ universities across 10+ countries — creating "
"opportunities for dual degrees, student exchange, and academic partnerships."
msgstr ""
"TIU 10 dan ortiq mamlakatdagi 40 dan ortiq universitet bilan hamkorlik "
"qiladi — qo'shma diplomlar, talaba almashinuvi va akademik hamkorlik "
"imkoniyatlarini yaratadi."

msgid "Countries"
msgstr "Mamlakatlar"

msgid "Dual Degree Programs"
msgstr "Qo'shma diplom dasturlari"

msgid "Network since"
msgstr "Hamkorlik boshlanishi"

msgid "South Korea"
msgstr "Janubiy Koreya"

msgid "Partnership Type"
msgstr "Hamkorlik turi"

msgid "Since"
msgstr "Yildan beri"

msgid "Memorandum"
msgstr "Memorandum"

msgid "Exchange"
msgstr "Almashinuv"

msgid "United States"
msgstr "AQSH"

msgid "Canada"
msgstr "Kanada"

msgid "Europe"
msgstr "Yevropa"

msgid "Country"
msgstr "Mamlakat"

msgid "Ireland"
msgstr "Irlandiya"

msgid "Spain"
msgstr "Ispaniya"

msgid "Cyprus"
msgstr "Kipr"

msgid "Turkey"
msgstr "Turkiya"

msgid "Malaysia"
msgstr "Malayziya"

msgid "Central Asia & Caucasus"
msgstr "Markaziy Osiyo va Kavkaz"

msgid "Kyrgyzstan"
msgstr "Qirg'iziston"

msgid "Kazakhstan"
msgstr "Qozog'iston"

msgid "Azerbaijan"
msgstr "Ozarbayjon"

msgid "Indonesia"
msgstr "Indoneziya"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"Expand your horizons — spend a semester or year at one of our partner "
"universities around the world."
msgstr ""
"Dunyoqarashingizni kengaytiring — sherik universitetlarimizdan birida bir "
"semestr yoki bir yil tahsil oling."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "What <em>exactly</em> does 'study abroad' mean?"
msgstr "<em>Aniq</em> aytganda, 'chet elda o'qish' nima degani?"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"It's a term used by universities to describe a range of international "
"opportunities — including semester exchanges, dual degree programmes, summer "
"schools, and academic field trips."
msgstr ""
"Bu universitetlar tomonidan turli xalqaro imkoniyatlarni — semestr "
"almashuvlari, qo'shma diplom dasturlari, yozgi maktablar va ilmiy "
"sayohatlarni ta'riflash uchun ishlatiladigan atama."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"At TIU, when we talk about 'study abroad', we typically mean our formal "
"Exchange Programme where you spend either a semester or a full academic year "
"studying at one of our partner universities around the world."
msgstr ""
"TIUda 'chet elda o'qish' deganda, biz odatda rasmiy Almashinuv dasturimizni "
"nazarda tutamiz — siz dunyodagi sherik universitetlarimizdan birida bir "
"semestr yoki to'liq o'quv yilini o'tkazasiz."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"Our International Office works with faculties to identify suitable partner "
"universities that complement and expand your studies here. Our growing "
"portfolio includes partners across South Korea, Europe, Turkey, and beyond."
msgstr ""
"Bizning Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi fakultetlar bilan birgalikda sizning "
"tahsilingizni to'ldiruvchi va kengaytiruvchi sherik universitetlarni "
"aniqlaydi. Rivojlanayotgan hamkorlik tarmog'imiz Janubiy Koreya, Yevropa, "
"Turkiya va boshqa mamlakatlarni o'z ichiga oladi."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Summer opportunities"
msgstr "Yozgi imkoniyatlar"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"We also offer other types of international experiences to our students that "
"don't have to be linked to your degree."
msgstr ""
"Shuningdek, biz talabalarga diplom dasturiga bog'liq bo'lmagan boshqa "
"turdagi xalqaro tajribalarni ham taklif etamiz."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "The benefits of studying abroad"
msgstr "Chet elda o'qishning afzalliklari"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Achieve better grades"
msgstr "Yuqoriroq natijaga erishing"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"with students who study abroad being more likely to graduate with higher "
"academic performance"
msgstr ""
"chet elda tahsil olgan talabalar yuqori akademik ko'rsatkichlar bilan "
"bitirish ehtimoli ko'proq bo'ladi"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Boost your career"
msgstr "Karyerangizni rivojlantiring"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"by developing skills in communication, adaptability, public speaking and more"
msgstr ""
"muloqot, moslashuvchanlik, ommaviy nutq va boshqa ko'nikmalarni "
"rivojlantirish orqali"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Earn more"
msgstr "Ko'proq daromad oling"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"with students who study abroad being more likely to have a higher wage after "
"graduation"
msgstr ""
"chet elda o'qigan talabalar bitirganidan keyin yuqoriroq maosh olish "
"ehtimoli ko'proq bo'ladi"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Funding is available"
msgstr "Moliyaviy yordam mavjud"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "to support your living and travel costs while studying abroad"
msgstr ""
"chet elda o'qish davomida yashash va sayohat xarajatlaringizni qoplash uchun"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Meet new people"
msgstr "Yangi odamlar bilan tanishing"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "and make lifelong connections with students from around the world"
msgstr "va butun dunyo talablari bilan umrbod do'stlik aloqalarini o'rnating"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Experience a new culture"
msgstr "Yangi madaniyatni his qiling"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "by immersing yourself in a different country, language, and way of life"
msgstr "boshqa mamlakat, til va turmush tarziga singib ketish orqali"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Learn a new language"
msgstr "Yangi til o'rganing"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"or improve existing skills through daily immersion in a multilingual "
"environment"
msgstr ""
"yoki ko'p tilli muhitda kundalik amaliyot orqali mavjud ko'nikmalaringizni "
"yaxshilang"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Gain confidence"
msgstr "O'zingizga ishonch hosil qiling"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"by stepping out of your comfort zone and building independence in a new "
"environment"
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"o'z konfort zonangizdan chiqib, yangi muhitda mustaqillikni shakllantirish "
"orqali\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"yangi muhitda o'z qulaylik zonangizdan chiqib, mustaqillik qurish orqali"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Semester abroad"
msgstr "Xorijda semestr"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"For our Business & Economics, Languages & Humanities, and IT & Engineering "
"programmes, study abroad is available for one semester. This is typically "
"integrated into the second year of your Bachelor's degree, allowing you to "
"gain international experience without extending your graduation timeline."
msgstr ""
"Bizning Biznes va Iqtisodiyot, Tillar va Gumanitar fanlar, IT va Muhandislik "
"dasturlarimiz uchun chet elda o'qish bir semestr davomida mavjud. Bu odatda "
"bakalavr darajangizning ikkinchi yiliga integratsiyalangan bo'lib, bitirish "
"muddatini uzaytirmasdan xalqaro tajriba orttirish imkonini beradi."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Year abroad"
msgstr "Xorijda bir yil"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"For other subjects that offer a study abroad option, this takes place over a "
"full academic year. This extends a standard undergraduate degree from four "
"to five years, with your year abroad taking place in year three. You'll then "
"return to complete the final year of your degree at TIU."
msgstr ""
"Chet elda o'qish imkoniyatini taklif etadigan boshqa fanlar uchun bu to'liq "
"o'quv yili davomida amalga oshiriladi. Bu standart bakalavr dasturini to'rt "
"yildan besh yilga uzaytiradi, chet eldagi yilingiz uchinchi yilda bo'ladi. "
"Keyin siz TIUda darajangizning oxirgi yilini tugatish uchun qaytasiz."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "If not here, then <em>where?</em>"
msgstr "Agar bu yerda bo'lmasa, <em>qayerda?</em>"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "We provide the opportunity; you decide the destination."
msgstr "Biz imkoniyat yaratamiz; manzilni siz tanlaysiz."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"With more than 10 partner universities around the globe to choose from, the "
"world is literally your oyster."
msgstr ""
"Dunyo bo'ylab 10 dan ortiq sherik universitetdan tanlash imkoniyati bilan "
"butun dunyo sizning oyoqlaringiz ostida."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But remember, our Exchange Programme is specific to your department and area "
"of study, so you'll need to choose an option that's available for your "
"subject."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Ammo esda tutingki, Almashinuv dasturimiz kafedrangiz va o'qish "
"yo'nalishingizga xos, shuning uchun fanlaringiz uchun mavjud bo'lgan "
"variantni tanlashingiz kerak bo'ladi.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Esda tutingki, Almashinuv dasturimiz fakultetingiz va o'qish "
"yo'nalishingizga xos, shuning uchun siz o'z faningiz uchun mavjud bo'lgan "
"variantni tanlashingiz kerak."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "TIU student studying abroad"
msgstr "Chet elda tahsil olayotgan TIU talabasi"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "TIU Study Abroad Programme"
msgstr "TIU Chet elda o'qish dasturi"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"It is easy to apply for the Study Abroad programme — just complete the "
"simple online application form during your second year. Don't worry if you "
"haven't selected a course with Study Abroad from the start, you will still "
"have time to transfer to this option."
msgstr ""
"Chet elda o'qish dasturiga ariza topshirish oson — ikkinchi yilingizda oddiy "
"onlayn ariza shaklini to'ldiring. Boshidanoq Chet elda o'qish bilan kursni "
"tanlamagan bo'lsangiz ham, bu variantga o'tish uchun vaqtingiz bo'ladi."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"Our International Office and Academic Coordinators offer personalised advice "
"and guidance on choosing the right destination, completing the application "
"process, and module selection."
msgstr ""
"Bizning Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi va Akademik koordinatorlar to'g'ri manzilni "
"tanlash, ariza jarayonini yakunlash va modul tanlash bo'yicha shaxsiy "
"maslahat va yo'l-yo'riq beradi."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"Studying abroad opens doors to new perspectives, skills, and lifelong "
"friendships. Take the step — it will be one of the best decisions of your "
"academic journey."
msgstr ""
"Chet elda o'qish yangi dunyoqarash, ko'nikmalar va umrbod do'stlikka eshik "
"ochadi. Qadam tashlang — bu akademik yo'lingizning eng yaxshi qarorlaridan "
"biri bo'ladi."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Study Abroad FAQs"
msgstr "Chet elda o'qish: ko'p beriladigan savollar"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Who is eligible to study abroad?"
msgstr "Chet elda o'qish uchun kim murojaat qilishi mumkin?"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All TIU students enrolled in a programme with a study abroad option are "
"eligible. You'll typically need to maintain a GPA of 2.5 or above and be in "
"good academic standing. Some partner universities may have additional "
"language requirements."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Chet elda o'qish imkoniyati bo'lgan dasturga ro'yxatdan o'tgan barcha TIU "
"talabalari murojaat qilishi mumkin. Odatda GPA 2.5 yoki undan yuqori "
"bo'lishi va yaxshi akademik ko'rsatkichga ega bo'lishingiz kerak. Ba'zi "
"sherik universitetlarda qo'shimcha til talablari bo'lishi mumkin.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Chet elda o'qish opsiyasi bo'lgan dasturga yozilgan barcha TIU talabalari "
"ariza topshira oladi. Odatda GPA 2.5 yoki undan yuqori bo'lishi va akademik "
"ko'rsatkichlar yaxshi bo'lishi kerak. Ba'zi hamkor universitetlarning "
"qo'shimcha til talablari bo'lishi mumkin."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Will I pay tuition at the partner university?"
msgstr "Sherik universitetda o'qish haqi to'layman-mi?"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"No. Exchange students continue to pay their regular TIU tuition fees. You "
"will not be charged tuition by the partner university. However, you will "
"need to cover your own living expenses, travel, and accommodation at the "
"host city."
msgstr ""
"Yo'q. Almashinuv talabalari oddiy TIU o'qish haqi to'lashni davom ettiradi. "
"Sherik universitet tomonidan o'qish haqi olinmaydi. Biroq, siz mezbonlik "
"shahridagi yashash, sayohat va turar joy xarajatlarini o'zingiz qoplashingiz "
"kerak."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Will my credits transfer back to TIU?"
msgstr "Kreditlarim TIUga o'tkaziladimi?"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"Yes. Before you go, you'll agree a learning plan with your Academic "
"Coordinator. The courses you take abroad will be mapped to TIU modules, and "
"your credits will transfer back once you've successfully completed them."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Ketishdan oldin Akademik koordinatoringiz bilan o'quv rejasini kelishib "
"olasiz. Chet elda o'tadigan kurslaringiz TIU modullariga moslashtiriladi va "
"ularni muvaffaqiyatli tugatganingizdan so'ng kreditlaringiz o'tkaziladi."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Can I choose which country I go to?"
msgstr "Qaysi mamlakatga borishimni o'zim tanlasam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"You can express a preference, but available destinations depend on your "
"department and programme. The International Office will present the options "
"available for your subject and help you choose the best fit."
msgstr ""
"O'z xohishingizni bildirishingiz mumkin, lekin mavjud manzillar kafedrangiz "
"va dasturingizga bog'liq. Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi fanlaringiz uchun mavjud "
"variantlarni taqdim etadi va eng mosini tanlashda yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "Is there funding or financial support available?"
msgstr "Moliyaviy yordam yoki grant mavjudmi?"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid ""
"Yes. TIU offers travel grants and exchange bursaries to help cover living "
"and travel costs. Some partner universities also offer additional support "
"for incoming exchange students. Contact the International Office for details."
msgstr ""
"Ha. TIU yashash va sayohat xarajatlarini qoplash uchun sayohat grantlari va "
"almashinuv stipendiyalarini taklif qiladi. Ba'zi sherik universitetlar ham "
"kelayotgan almashinuv talabalari uchun qo'shimcha yordam beradi. Batafsil "
"ma'lumot uchun Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limiga murojaat qiling."

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
msgid "When do I need to apply?"
msgstr "Qachon ariza topshirishim kerak?"

#: templates/pages/international/study-abroad.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Applications typically open in October for the following academic year. "
"Deadlines vary by destination, but most close by February. Apply early to "
"secure your preferred destination — places are limited."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Arizalar odatda keyingi o'quv yili uchun oktyabr oyida ochiladi. Muddatlar "
"manzilga qarab farq qiladi, lekin ko'pchiligi fevral oyida yopiladi. "
"Xohlagan manzilingizni ta'minlash uchun erta ariza topshing — o'rinlar "
"cheklangan.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Arizalar odatda oktyabrda keyingi o'quv yili uchun ochiladi. Muddatlar "
"yo'nalishga qarab farq qiladi, lekin ko'pchiligi fevralda yopiladi. Afzal "
"ko'rgan yo'nalishingizni ta'minlash uchun erta ariza topshiring — o'rinlar "
"cheklangan."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Exchange Opportunities - International | TIU"
msgstr "Almashinuv imkoniyatlari - Xalqaro | TIU"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Discover semester exchanges, summer schools, and international programmes "
"available to TIU students."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalariga taqdim etiladigan semestrlik almashinuv, yozgi maktablar va "
"xalqaro dasturlarni kashf eting."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Why come to TIU?"
msgstr "Nima uchun TIUga kelish kerak?"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A proud history, academic excellence, and a destination filled with "
"opportunity."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Boy tarix, akademik mukammallik va imkoniyatlarga to'la muhit.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Faxrli tarix, akademik mukammallik va imkoniyatlarga boy yo'nalish."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"You'll be part of a diverse student community and have the chance to study "
"and socialise on a safe and friendly campus that has everything you need in "
"one place. If you want to explore further afield, Tashkent's historic Silk "
"Road landmarks and vibrant bazaars await. And as one of the most affordable "
"cities in Central Asia, your money goes further here."
msgstr ""
"Siz xilma-xil talabalar jamoasining a'zosi bo'lasiz va xavfsiz hamda "
"do'stona kampusda o'qish va muloqot qilish imkoniyatiga ega bo'lasiz. Agar "
"yanada ko'proq joylarni o'rganmoqchi bo'lsangiz, Toshkentning tarixiy Ipak "
"yo'li obidalari va jonli bozorlari sizni kutmoqda. Markaziy Osiyodagi eng "
"arzon shaharlardan biri sifatida, pulingiz bu yerda ancha uzoqqa yetadi."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Explore Central Asia while you study"
msgstr "O'qish davomida Markaziy Osiyoni kashf eting"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Tashkent has great transport links making it easy to visit Samarkand, "
"Bukhara, and other historic cities during your time with us."
msgstr ""
"Toshkentning qulay transport aloqalari tufayli biz bilan bo'lgan davrda "
"Samarqand, Buxoro va boshqa tarixiy shaharlarni osongina ziyorat qilishingiz "
"mumkin."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Study in English from day one"
msgstr "Birinchi kundan ingliz tilida o'qing"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"All exchange courses are delivered in English. No Uzbek language requirement "
"— though you're welcome to learn along the way."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Barcha almashinuv kurslari ingliz tilida o'tiladi. O'zbek tilini bilish "
"talab etilmaydi — lekin yo'l-yo'lakay o'rganishingiz mumkin.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Barcha almashinuv darslari ingliz tilida olib boriladi. O'zbek tilini bilish "
"talab qilinmaydi — lekin o'rganishni xohlasangiz, doimo xush kelibsiz."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Affordable student living"
msgstr "Arzon talabalar turmushi"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Tashkent is one of the most affordable student cities in Asia. A full meal "
"costs around $3, and rent starts from $200 per month."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent Osiyodagi eng arzon talabalar shaharlaridan biri. To'liq ovqat "
"taxminan 3 dollarga tushadi, ijara narxi esa oyiga 200 dollardan boshlanadi."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "A welcoming international community"
msgstr "Mehmon do'st xalqaro jamoa"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Join students from across Central Asia, South Korea, Turkey, Europe, and "
"beyond. Our campus is built on diversity and inclusion."
msgstr ""
"Markaziy Osiyo, Janubiy Koreya, Turkiya, Yevropa va boshqa mamlakatlardan "
"kelgan talabalarga qo'shiling. Bizning kampusimiz xilma-xillik va "
"inklyuzivlik asosida qurilgan."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Safe and supportive environment"
msgstr "Xavfsiz va qo'llab-quvvatlovchi muhit"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Tashkent is ranked among the safest capitals in the region. Our "
"International Office provides full support from arrival to departure."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent mintaqadagi eng xavfsiz poytaxtlar qatoriga kiradi. Xalqaro "
"aloqalar bo'limimiz kelishdan ketishgacha to'liq yordam ko'rsatadi."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Ways to experience TIU"
msgstr "TIUni boshdan kechirish yo'llari"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Exchange student programme"
msgstr "Almashinuv talabasi dasturi"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"If your institution has an exchange agreement with us, you can come to TIU "
"as an international exchange student. You'll study alongside our degree "
"students for one or two semesters, with full access to campus facilities and "
"student life."
msgstr ""
"Agar sizning muassasangiz biz bilan almashinuv shartnomasiga ega bo'lsa, "
"TIUga xalqaro almashinuv talabasi sifatida kelishingiz mumkin. Bir yoki ikki "
"semestr davomida bizning darajali talabalarimiz bilan birga o'qiysiz, kampus "
"imkoniyatlari va talabalar hayotidan to'liq foydalanasiz."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Visiting student programme"
msgstr "Mehmon talaba dasturi"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"If your university does not have an exchange agreement, you can still apply "
"directly to TIU as an international visiting student. Choose from a range of "
"modules across our faculties and earn credits that transfer back to your "
"home institution."
msgstr ""
"Agar universitetingizning almashinuv shartnomasi bo'lmasa, TIUga xalqaro "
"mehmon talaba sifatida bevosita ariza topshirishingiz mumkin. "
"Fakultetlarimizdagi turli modullardan tanlang va o'z muassasangizga "
"o'tkaziladigan kreditlarni to'plang."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Not sure which applies to you?"
msgstr "Qaysi dastur sizga mos ekanligini bilmayapsizmi?"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Contact our team at <a href=\"mailto:international@tiu."
"uz\">international@tiu.uz</a> and we'll be happy to help."
msgstr ""
"Jamoamizga <a href=\"mailto:international@tiu.uz\">international@tiu.uz</a> "
"orqali murojaat qiling, biz yordam berishdan mamnun bo'lamiz."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Exchange FAQs"
msgstr "Almashinuv bo'yicha savol-javoblar"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Does my university need a partnership with TIU?"
msgstr "Universitetimning TIU bilan hamkorlik shartnomasi bo'lishi kerakmi?"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"For the Exchange Student Programme, yes — your home university must have an "
"active exchange agreement with TIU. If there is no agreement, you can still "
"apply through our Visiting Student Programme, which is open to students from "
"any accredited university."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv talabasi dasturi uchun ha — sizning universitetingiz TIU bilan "
"amaldagi almashinuv shartnomasiga ega bo'lishi kerak. Shartnoma bo'lmasa, "
"har qanday akkreditatsiyalangan universitetning talabalariga ochiq bo'lgan "
"Mehmon talaba dasturimiz orqali ariza topshirishingiz mumkin."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "How long can I study at TIU on exchange?"
msgstr "TIUda almashinuv dasturi bo'yicha qancha vaqt o'qishim mumkin?"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Exchange students can study at TIU for one semester (autumn or spring) or a "
"full academic year. The duration depends on your home university's agreement "
"with TIU and your own academic plan."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv talabalari TIUda bir semestr (kuz yoki bahor) yoki to'liq o'quv "
"yili davomida o'qishlari mumkin. Muddat sizning universitetingizning TIU "
"bilan kelishuvi va shaxsiy o'quv rejangizga bog'liq."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Do I pay tuition fees to TIU?"
msgstr "TIUga o'quv to'lovini to'lashim kerakmi?"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Exchange students continue to pay tuition to their home university — no "
"additional tuition is charged by TIU. Visiting students may be subject to a "
"separate fee; contact the International Office for details."
msgstr ""
"Almashinuv talabalari o'quv to'lovini o'z universitetlariga to'lashda davom "
"etadi — TIU tomonidan qo'shimcha to'lov olinmaydi. Mehmon talabalar uchun "
"alohida to'lov bo'lishi mumkin; batafsil ma'lumot uchun Xalqaro aloqalar "
"bo'limiga murojaat qiling."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "Will my credits transfer back to my home university?"
msgstr "Kreditlarim o'z universitetimga o'tkaziladimi?"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Yes. Before arriving, you'll agree a learning agreement with both TIU and "
"your home university. The courses you complete at TIU will be mapped to "
"equivalent credits at your institution. We use the ECTS credit system for "
"easy transfer."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Kelishdan oldin TIU va o'z universitetingiz bilan o'quv shartnomasi "
"tuzasiz. TIUda tugatgan kurslaringiz muassasangizdagi teng kreditlarga mos "
"keltiriladi. Oson o'tkazish uchun ECTS kredit tizimidan foydalanamiz."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "What support does TIU offer exchange students?"
msgstr "TIU almashinuv talabalariga qanday yordam ko'rsatadi?"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"Our International Office provides full support — from visa and accommodation "
"assistance to airport pickup, orientation, and a buddy programme pairing you "
"with a local student. You'll have access to all campus facilities, student "
"clubs, and events."
msgstr ""
"Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limimiz to'liq yordam ko'rsatadi — viza va turar joy "
"masalalaridan aeroportda kutib olish, yo'naltirish va sizni mahalliy talaba "
"bilan juftlashtiruvchi do'stlik dasturigacha. Barcha kampus imkoniyatlari, "
"talabalar klublari va tadbirlarga kirish huquqiga ega bo'lasiz."

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid "When should I apply?"
msgstr "Qachon ariza topshirishim kerak?"

#: templates/pages/international/exchange-opportunities.html
msgid ""
"For the autumn semester, apply by 1 May. For the spring semester, apply by 1 "
"November. Applications are submitted through your home university's exchange "
"coordinator, who will liaise with our International Office."
msgstr ""
"Kuzgi semestr uchun 1 maygacha ariza topshing. Bahorgi semestr uchun 1 "
"noyabrgacha ariza topshing. Arizalar universitetingizning almashinuv "
"koordinatori orqali topshiriladi, u bizning Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limimiz "
"bilan bog'lanadi."

