msgid "Exam Rules"
msgstr "Imtihon qoidalari"

msgid ""
"Everything you need to know about the examination process — rules, schedule, "
"grading, and what to do if something goes wrong."
msgstr ""
"Imtihon jarayoni haqida bilishingiz kerak bo'lgan hamma narsa — qoidalar, "
"jadval, baholash va kutilmagan holatlarda nima qilish."

msgid "Know the rules."
msgstr "Qoidalarni biling."

msgid "Be prepared."
msgstr "Tayyor bo'ling."

msgid ""
"Examinations at TIU are conducted in strict accordance with university "
"regulations. Every student is expected to follow the rules of academic "
"integrity and be familiar with the exam procedures before the examination "
"period begins."
msgstr ""
"TIU da imtihonlar universitet qoidalariga qat'iy muvofiq o'tkaziladi. Har "
"bir talaba akademik halollik qoidalariga rioya qilishi va imtihon davri "
"boshlanishidan oldin tartib bilan tanish bo'lishi kutiladi."

msgid ""
"Exams are held twice per semester — midterm exams during the semester and "
"final exams at the end. The exam schedule is published at least two weeks "
"before the examination period starts."
msgstr ""
"Imtihonlar har semestrda ikki marta o'tkaziladi — semestr davomida oraliq "
"imtihonlar va oxirida yakuniy imtihonlar. Imtihon jadvali kamida ikki hafta "
"oldin e'lon qilinadi."

msgid "Questions about exams?"
msgstr "Imtihonlar bo'yicha savollaringiz bormi?"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Contact the Academic Affairs office or your department head for any exam-"
"related questions."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Imtihon bilan bog'liq har qanday savol uchun O'quv ishlari bo'limi yoki "
"kafedra mudiri bilan bog'laning.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Imtihonga oid har qanday savol uchun O'quv ishlari bo'limi yoki fakultet "
"boshlig'ingizga murojaat qiling."

msgid "General Exam Rules"
msgstr "Umumiy imtihon qoidalari"

msgid "All students must follow these rules during examinations:"
msgstr ""
"Barcha talabalar imtihon davomida quyidagi qoidalarga rioya qilishi shart:"

msgid "Arrive at least 15 minutes before the exam starts"
msgstr "Imtihon boshlanishidan kamida 15 daqiqa oldin keling"

msgid "Bring a valid student ID — you will not be admitted without it"
msgstr "Talaba guvohnomangizni olib keling — usiz kiritilmaysiz"

msgid ""
"Mobile phones and smart devices must be switched off and left at the front "
"of the room"
msgstr "Telefon va qurilmalar o'chirilgan holda xona oldiga qo'yilishi kerak"

msgid ""
"No talking, whispering, or any form of communication with other students "
"during the exam"
msgstr ""
"Imtihon davomida gaplashish, shivirlash yoki boshqa talabalar bilan aloqa "
"qilish taqiqlanadi"

msgid ""
"Only materials approved by the instructor are allowed (calculator, "
"dictionary, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"Faqat o'qituvchi ruxsat bergan materiallar (kalkulyator, lug'at va h.k.) "
"ruxsat etiladi"

msgid ""
"Students caught cheating will receive a zero grade and face disciplinary "
"action"
msgstr ""
"Ko'chirish ustida ushlangan talabalar nol baho oladi va intizomiy jazo "
"ko'radi"

msgid ""
"You may not leave the exam room during the first 30 minutes or the last 15 "
"minutes"
msgstr ""
"Birinchi 30 daqiqa va oxirgi 15 daqiqada imtihon xonasidan chiqish mumkin "
"emas"

msgid "Exam Schedule"
msgstr "Imtihon jadvali"

msgid "MIDTERM EXAMS"
msgstr "ORALIQ IMTIHONLAR"

msgid "Held during weeks 7-8 of each semester"
msgstr "Har semestrning 7-8 haftalarida o'tkaziladi"

msgid "FINAL EXAMS"
msgstr "YAKUNIY IMTIHONLAR"

msgid "Held during the last 2-3 weeks of each semester"
msgstr "Har semestrning oxirgi 2-3 haftasida o'tkaziladi"

msgid "RESIT EXAMS"
msgstr "QAYTA TOPSHIRISH"

msgid "July — for students who failed or missed exams with valid reason"
msgstr ""
"Iyul — imtihondan o'ta olmagan yoki uzrli sabab bilan o'tkazib yuborgan "
"talabalar uchun"

msgid "RESULTS"
msgstr "NATIJALAR"

msgid "Published within 5 working days after the exam on the student portal"
msgstr "Imtihondan keyin 5 ish kuni ichida talabalar portalida e'lon qilinadi"

msgid "Grading System"
msgstr "Baholash tizimi"

msgid "TIU uses a 100-point grading scale with the following breakdown:"
msgstr "TIU 100 ballik baholash tizimidan foydalanadi:"

msgid "86-100 points — Excellent"
msgstr "86-100 ball — A'lo"

msgid "71-85 points — Good"
msgstr "71-85 ball — Yaxshi"

msgid "56-70 points — Satisfactory"
msgstr "56-70 ball — Qoniqarli"

msgid "0-55 points — Unsatisfactory"
msgstr "0-55 ball — Qoniqarsiz"

msgid ""
"The final grade consists of: coursework (40%) + midterm exam (20%) + final "
"exam (40%)."
msgstr ""
"Yakuniy baho: joriy baholash (40%) + oraliq imtihon (20%) + yakuniy imtihon "
"(40%)."

msgid "Exam FAQs"
msgstr "Imtihon savollari"

msgid "What happens if I miss an exam?"
msgstr "Imtihonni o'tkazib yuborsam nima bo'ladi?"

msgid ""
"If you miss an exam due to illness or emergency, you must submit a valid "
"document (medical certificate or official letter) to the Academic Affairs "
"office within 3 working days. If approved, you will be allowed to take the "
"exam during the resit period in July."
msgstr ""
"Kasallik yoki favqulodda holat sababli imtihonni o'tkazib yuborsangiz, 3 ish "
"kuni ichida O'quv ishlari bo'limiga hujjat topshirishingiz kerak. "
"Tasdiqlansa, iyuldagi qayta topshirish davrida imtihon topshirishga ruxsat "
"beriladi."

msgid "Can I appeal my exam grade?"
msgstr "Imtihon bahosiga e'tiroz bildirsam bo'ladimi?"

msgid ""
"Yes. You can submit a written appeal to the Academic Affairs office within 3 "
"days of the results being published. A review committee will re-evaluate "
"your exam paper and notify you of the outcome within 5 working days."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Natijalar e'lon qilinganidan keyin 3 kun ichida O'quv ishlari bo'limiga "
"yozma ariza topshirishingiz mumkin. Komissiya imtihon ishingizni qayta "
"ko'rib chiqadi va 5 ish kuni ichida natijani bildiradi."

msgid "What counts as cheating?"
msgstr "Nima ko'chirish hisoblanadi?"

msgid ""
"Cheating includes: using unauthorized notes or devices, copying from another "
"student, sharing answers, submitting someone else's work as your own, or any "
"attempt to gain an unfair advantage. All cases are investigated by the "
"Disciplinary Committee."
msgstr ""
"Ko'chirish: ruxsatsiz eslatma yoki qurilma ishlatish, boshqa talabadan nusxa "
"ko'chirish, javoblarni almashish, boshqaning ishini o'zingizniki deb "
"topshirish. Barcha holatlar Intizom komissiyasi tomonidan tekshiriladi."

msgid "How does the resit exam work?"
msgstr "Qayta topshirish qanday ishlaydi?"

msgid ""
"Resit exams are held in July for students who received an unsatisfactory "
"grade (D) or missed the original exam with a valid reason. You can retake up "
"to 3 exams during the resit period. The resit grade replaces the original "
"grade."
msgstr ""
"Qayta topshirish imtihonlari iyulda o'tkaziladi — qoniqarsiz baho olgan yoki "
"uzrli sabab bilan o'tkazib yuborgan talabalar uchun. 3 tagacha imtihon qayta "
"topshirish mumkin. Yangi baho eski bahoni almashtiradi."

