msgid "CAN'T FIND WHAT YOU'RE LOOKING FOR?"
msgstr "QIDIRAYOTGAN NARSANGIZNI TOPA OLMADINGIZMI?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Start your own club or society"
msgstr "O'z klubingizni yarating"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"Don't see anything that suits you? At TIU, you can start your own club with "
"just a few friends. As a young university, we encourage every student "
"initiative — all you need is 3 members and a good idea."
msgstr ""
"O'zingizga mos narsa topa olmadingizmi? TIUda bir necha do'stingiz bilan o'z "
"klubingizni ochishingiz mumkin. Yosh universitet sifatida biz har bir talaba "
"tashabbusini qo'llab-quvvatlaymiz — sizga faqat 3 a'zo va yaxshi g'oya kerak."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"Whether it's a robotics club, a book circle, a music group, or anything else "
"you're passionate about — talk to our Student Affairs office and make it "
"happen."
msgstr ""
"Robototexnika klubi, kitob to'garagi, musiqa guruhi yoki boshqa qiziqarli "
"narsa bo'lsin — Talabalar ishlari bo'limiga murojaat qiling va amalga "
"oshiring."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "New clubs are launching every semester. Yours could be next."
msgstr ""
"Har semestrda yangi klublar ochilmoqda. Keyingisi sizniki bo'lishi mumkin."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"TIU's Student Union represents the voice of all students. Every enrolled "
"student is automatically a member — no fees, no sign-up needed."
msgstr ""
"TIU Talabalar kengashi barcha talabalarning ovozini ifodalaydi. Har bir "
"ro'yxatdan o'tgan talaba avtomatik ravishda a'zo bo'ladi — to'lov yoki "
"ro'yxatdan o'tish talab etilmaydi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union organizes events, supports club activities, and ensures "
"students have a say in university life. It's your platform to lead, "
"collaborate, and make a difference."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar kengashi tadbirlar tashkil etadi, klub faoliyatini qo'llab-"
"quvvatlaydi va talabalarning universitet hayotida o'z so'zini aytishini "
"ta'minlaydi. Bu sizning boshchilik qilish, hamkorlik qilish va o'zgarish "
"yaratish uchun platformangiz."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid ""
"From cultural events and sports days to community projects, the Student "
"Union is at the heart of campus life at TIU."
msgstr ""
"Madaniy tadbirlar va sport kunlaridan jamoa loyihalarigacha — Talabalar "
"kengashi TIU kampus hayotining markazida turadi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Visit TIU Student Union"
msgstr "TIU Talabalar kengashiga tashrif buyuring"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "Club"
msgstr "Klub"

#: templates/pages/current-students/clubs.html
msgid "TIU Student Union"
msgstr "TIU Talabalar kengashi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Stay active and healthy with TIU's growing sports facilities, fitness "
"classes, and inter-faculty competitions."
msgstr ""
"TIUning rivojlanayotgan sport inshootlari, fitnes mashg'ulotlari va "
"fakultetlararo musobaqalari bilan faol va sog'lom bo'ling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Move more, achieve more"
msgstr "Ko'proq harakat qiling, ko'proq natijalarga erishing"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"TIU is a young university, founded in 2023, and our sports programme is "
"growing every semester. Whether you are a seasoned athlete or just looking "
"to stay fit between lectures, there is a place for you here."
msgstr ""
"TIU 2023-yilda tashkil etilgan yosh universitet bo'lib, sport dasturimiz har "
"semestrda rivojlanib bormoqda. Tajribali sportchi bo'lasizmi yoki ma'ruzalar "
"orasida sog'lom bo'lishni xohlaysizmi — bu yerda siz uchun joy bor."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"We offer football, basketball, volleyball, table tennis, and regular fitness "
"classes. Our students take part in inter-faculty tournaments and friendly "
"matches with other Tashkent universities. No experience required — just "
"bring your energy."
msgstr ""
"Biz futbol, basketbol, voleybol, stol tennisi va muntazam fitnes "
"mashg'ulotlarini taklif etamiz. Talabalarimiz fakultetlararo musobaqalarda "
"va Toshkentdagi boshqa universitetlar bilan do'stona o'yinlarda ishtirok "
"etishadi. Tajriba talab qilinmaydi — faqat shijoatingizni olib keling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Our Teams"
msgstr "Bizning jamoalar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Sport is for everyone at TIU"
msgstr "TIUda sport — hamma uchun"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"You do not need to be a professional to join. Our teams train regularly in "
"the multi-court hall and outdoor pitches. From inter-faculty football "
"tournaments to table tennis leagues, there are plenty of ways to compete and "
"have fun."
msgstr ""
"Qo'shilish uchun professional bo'lishingiz shart emas. Jamoalarimiz ko'p "
"maqsadli sport zalida va ochiq maydonchalarda muntazam mashq qiladi. "
"Fakultetlararo futbol musobaqalaridan stol tennisi ligalarigacha — "
"raqobatlashish va zavqlanish uchun ko'plab imkoniyatlar mavjud."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Explore Clubs & Societies"
msgstr "Klublar va jamiyatlarni ko'ring"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Our facilities"
msgstr "Bizning sport inshootlari"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As a growing university, we are steadily expanding our sports "
"infrastructure. All facilities are available to TIU students free of charge."
msgstr ""
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Rivojlanayotgan universitet sifatida biz sport infratuzilmamizni izchil "
"kengaytirib bormoqdamiz. Barcha sport inshootlari TIU talabalari uchun "
"bepul.\n"
"#-#-#-#-#  django.po (TIU Website 1.0)  #-#-#-#-#\n"
"Rivojlanayotgan universitet sifatida biz sport infratuzilmamizni izchil "
"kengaytirib bormoqdamiz. Barcha sport inshootlari TIU talabalariga bepul."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Gym with cardio equipment and free weights"
msgstr "Kardio jihozlar va erkin og'irliklar bilan jihozlangan sport zali"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Multi-court hall for basketball, volleyball, and futsal"
msgstr "Basketbol, voleybol va futsal uchun ko'p maqsadli sport zali"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Outdoor football and mini-football pitches"
msgstr "Ochiq futbol va mini-futbol maydonchalari"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Table tennis room"
msgstr "Stol tennisi xonasi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Changing rooms and showers"
msgstr "Kiyinish xonalari va dushlar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "How to get involved"
msgstr "Qanday qo'shilish mumkin"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Getting started is easy — no tryouts, no pressure. Just show up."
msgstr "Boshlash oson — sinov yo'q, bosim yo'q. Shunchaki keling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Check the schedule"
msgstr "Jadvalni tekshiring"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Training times and fitness class schedules are posted on the LMS portal and "
"the sports noticeboard in Building B."
msgstr ""
"Mashg'ulot vaqtlari va fitnes darslar jadvali LMS portalida va B binodagi "
"sport e'lonlar taxtasida joylashtirilgan."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Turn up"
msgstr "Keling"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Most sessions are open to everyone. Just come to the sports hall or gym at "
"the listed time — no registration needed."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pchilik mashg'ulotlar hamma uchun ochiq. Belgilangan vaqtda sport zaliga "
"yoki trenajyor zaliga keling — ro'yxatdan o'tish shart emas."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Join a team"
msgstr "Jamoaga qo'shiling"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"If you want to compete in inter-faculty tournaments, speak to the team "
"captain or the Sports Coordinator to join the squad."
msgstr ""
"Fakultetlararo musobaqalarda ishtirok etmoqchi bo'lsangiz, jamoa sardori "
"yoki Sport koordinatoriga murojaat qilib jamoaga qo'shiling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Sports FAQs"
msgstr "Sport bo'yicha tez-tez beriladigan savollar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Do I need experience to join a sports team?"
msgstr "Sport jamoasiga qo'shilish uchun tajriba kerakmi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Not at all. Our teams welcome all skill levels. Recreational sessions are "
"open to complete beginners, and regular training sessions will help you "
"improve quickly."
msgstr ""
"Umuman yo'q. Jamoalarimiz barcha darajadagi sportchilarni qabul qiladi. Dam "
"olish mashg'ulotlari yangi boshlovchilar uchun ochiq, muntazam mashqlar esa "
"tezda rivojlanishingizga yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Are sports facilities free for students?"
msgstr "Sport inshootlari talabalar uchun bepulmi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Yes. All on-campus sports facilities are free for enrolled TIU students. "
"Just bring your student ID card."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Kampusdagi barcha sport inshootlari TIU talabalari uchun bepul. Faqat "
"talaba guvohnomangizni olib keling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "What are the opening hours?"
msgstr "Ish vaqti qanday?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"The gym and sports hall are open Monday to Saturday, 08:00–21:00. Team "
"training sessions are usually held in the evenings, 17:00–20:00. Morning "
"exercise sessions start at 07:30 on weekdays."
msgstr ""
"Sport zali va trenajyor zali dushanba–shanba kunlari 08:00–21:00 gacha "
"ochiq. Jamoa mashqlari odatda kechqurun 17:00–20:00 da o'tkaziladi. "
"Ertalabki mashqlar ish kunlari soat 07:30 da boshlanadi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid "Can I start a new sports team?"
msgstr "Yangi sport jamoasini tashkil qilsam bo'ladimi?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/sports.html
msgid ""
"Yes. If you have at least 5 interested students, you can propose a new team "
"through the Student Union. The Sports Coordinator will help you arrange "
"training slots and equipment."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Kamida 5 nafar qiziquvchi talaba bo'lsa, Talabalar kengashi orqali yangi "
"jamoa taklif qilishingiz mumkin. Sport koordinatori mashq vaqtlari va "
"jihozlarni tashkil qilishda yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Your voice on campus — learn about the Student Union and how to get involved."
msgstr ""
"Kampusdagi ovozingiz — Talabalar Kengashi haqida bilib oling va faol bo'ling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "What is the Student Union?"
msgstr "Talabalar Kengashi nima?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Tashkent International University's Student Union — Talabalar Kengashi — is "
"the student-led body that represents all TIU students. Founded alongside the "
"university in 2023, the Student Union is still young and growing, just like "
"TIU itself."
msgstr ""
"Toshkent xalqaro universitetining Talabalar Kengashi — bu barcha TIU "
"talabalarini ifodalovchi, talabalar tomonidan boshqariladigan tashkilotdir. "
"2023-yilda universitet bilan birga tashkil etilgan Talabalar Kengashi hali "
"yosh va rivojlanmoqda — xuddi TIU ning o'zi kabi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Our mission is simple: represent student interests, organize memorable "
"events, and serve as a bridge between students and the university "
"administration. Every enrolled student is automatically a member."
msgstr ""
"Bizning maqsadimiz oddiy: talabalar manfaatlarini himoya qilish, esda "
"qolarli tadbirlar tashkil etish va talabalar bilan universitet ma'muriyati "
"o'rtasida ko'prik bo'lib xizmat qilish. Har bir ro'yxatga olingan talaba "
"avtomatik ravishda a'zo hisoblanadi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union is where your ideas turn into real campus life. We are a "
"small but active team, and every student voice matters."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi — bu sizning g'oyalaringiz haqiqiy kampus hayotiga "
"aylanadigan joy. Biz kichik, lekin faol jamoamiz va har bir talabaning ovozi "
"muhim."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Sardor Alimov"
msgstr "Sardor Alimov"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "President of Student Union 2025/26"
msgstr "Talabalar Kengashi raisi 2025/26"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "For"
msgstr "Uchun"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "students,"
msgstr "talabalar,"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "by"
msgstr "tomonidan"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "students"
msgstr "talabalar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union is run entirely by students. Our elected leaders work "
"closely with the university administration to voice your concerns, improve "
"campus life, and make sure every student feels heard. Anyone can run for a "
"leadership role — no experience required, just passion."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi to'liq talabalar tomonidan boshqariladi. Saylangan "
"rahbarlarimiz sizning tashvishlaringizni bildirish, kampus hayotini "
"yaxshilash va har bir talabaning ovozi eshitilishini ta'minlash uchun "
"universitet ma'muriyati bilan yaqin hamkorlik qiladi. Har kim rahbarlik "
"lavozimiga nomzod bo'lishi mumkin — tajriba shart emas, faqat ishtiyoq kerak."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "TIU Student Union members"
msgstr "TIU Talabalar Kengashi a'zolari"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Meet new people, make lasting friendships"
msgstr "Yangi odamlar bilan tanishing, mustahkam do'stlik o'rnating"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Join a club, play sports, or volunteer — these are the best ways to find "
"your people at TIU. We have a growing number of student clubs, sports teams, "
"and creative groups. You can also start your own."
msgstr ""
"Klubga qo'shiling, sport bilan shug'ullaning yoki ko'ngillilik qiling — TIU "
"da o'z odamlaringizni topishning eng yaxshi yo'llari shu. Talabalar "
"klublari, sport jamoalari va ijodiy guruhlar soni ortib bormoqda. O'zingiz "
"ham yangi guruh tashkil qilishingiz mumkin."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Make your voice heard"
msgstr "Ovozingizni eshittiring"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union represents your interests — from course feedback to "
"university decisions. Attend Student Council meetings, vote in elections, or "
"run for a leadership position yourself."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi sizning manfaatlaringizni ifodalaydi — kurs bo'yicha fikr-"
"mulohazalardan tortib universitet qarorlarigacha. Talabalar kengashi "
"yig'ilishlarida qatnashing, saylovlarda ovoz bering yoki o'zingiz rahbarlik "
"lavozimiga nomzod bo'ling."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Get involved"
msgstr "Faol bo'ling"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Events that bring campus to life"
msgstr "Kampusni jonlantiradigan tadbirlar"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"From Navro'z celebrations and sport tournaments to cultural evenings and end-"
"of-year festivities — the Student Union organizes events throughout the year "
"that make student life unforgettable."
msgstr ""
"Navro'z bayramlari va sport musobaqalaridan madaniy kechalar va yil "
"yakunidagi tantanalargacha — Talabalar Kengashi yil davomida talabalar "
"hayotini unutilmas qiladigan tadbirlar tashkil etadi."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "View events"
msgstr "Tadbirlarni ko'rish"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Connect with university administration"
msgstr "Universitet ma'muriyati bilan aloqa"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union serves as your direct link to the university "
"administration. If you have questions, concerns, or ideas — we bring them to "
"the table on your behalf."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi sizning universitet ma'muriyati bilan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"aloqangiz hisoblanadi. Savollaringiz, tashvishlaringiz yoki g'oyalaringiz "
"bo'lsa — biz ularni sizning nomingizdan yetkazamiz."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Get support"
msgstr "Yordam olish"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Where to find the Student Union on campus?"
msgstr "Kampusda Talabalar Kengashini qayerda topish mumkin?"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"The Student Union office is located in the main building. Drop by during "
"working hours — our team is always happy to chat, answer questions, or hear "
"your ideas for campus life."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar Kengashi ofisi asosiy binoda joylashgan. Ish vaqtida tashrif "
"buyuring — jamoamiz har doim suhbatlashishga, savollarga javob berishga yoki "
"kampus hayoti bo'yicha g'oyalaringizni eshitishga tayyor."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "FOLLOW TIUSU"
msgstr "TIUSU NI KUZATING"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "TIU Student Union building"
msgstr "TIU Talabalar Kengashi binosi"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Visit TIU"
msgstr "TIU ga tashrif buyuring"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "you get here"
msgstr "kelishingizdan oldin"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid ""
"Take a virtual tour of our modern campus, student spaces, and Tashkent "
"itself: a city that combines rich history with a vibrant student scene. "
"There's lots to see and loads to do. So, let's get going..."
msgstr ""
"Zamonaviy kampusimiz, talabalar makonlari va Toshkent shahrining virtual "
"sayohatiga chiqing: boy tarixi va jonli talabalar muhitini birlashtirgan "
"shahar. Ko'rish va qilish uchun juda ko'p narsa bor. Xo'sh, boshlaylik..."

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "Start your virtual tour now"
msgstr "Virtual sayohatingizni hozir boshlang"

#: templates/pages/current-students/student-union.html
msgid "TIU campus life"
msgstr "TIU kampus hayoti"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Helping TIU students prepare for their first professional steps — with CV "
"support, interview coaching, and direct employer connections."
msgstr ""
"TIU talabalariga birinchi professional qadamlarini qo'yishda yordam berish — "
"rezyume tayyorlash, intervyuga tayyorgarlik va ish beruvchilar bilan "
"bevosita aloqalar."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Find your path from the start"
msgstr "Boshidanoq o'z yo'lingizni toping"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"TIU was founded in 2023, and our Career Center has been part of the journey "
"since the very beginning. We believe career preparation should start early — "
"not after graduation."
msgstr ""
"TIU 2023-yilda tashkil etilgan va Karyera markazi boshidanoq universitetning "
"bir qismi bo'lib kelmoqda. Biz karyeraga tayyorgarlikni erta boshlash kerak "
"deb hisoblaymiz — bitirganidan keyin emas."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Our small but dedicated team works with every student individually, offering "
"practical guidance on building a strong CV, preparing for interviews, and "
"understanding what employers in Uzbekistan are looking for."
msgstr ""
"Bizning kichik, lekin fidoyi jamoamiz har bir talaba bilan individual "
"ishlaydi — kuchli rezyume tayyorlash, intervyuga tayyorgarlik va "
"O'zbekistondagi ish beruvchilar nimani izlayotganini tushuntirish bo'yicha "
"amaliy maslahatlar beradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"We organise regular CV workshops, mock interview sessions, and career "
"counseling meetings to help you feel confident and ready when opportunities "
"come your way."
msgstr ""
"Biz muntazam ravishda rezyume tayyorlash seminarlari, sinov intervyular va "
"karyera bo'yicha maslahat uchrashuvlarini o'tkazamiz — imkoniyatlar "
"kelganida o'zingizga ishonchli va tayyor bo'lishingiz uchun."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Whether you are looking for an internship, part-time work, or simply want to "
"explore your options — our door is always open."
msgstr ""
"Amaliyot izlayotgan bo'lsangiz, yarim stavkali ish yoki shunchaki "
"imkoniyatlaringizni o'rganmoqchi bo'lsangiz — eshigimiz doimo ochiq."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "CV workshops"
msgstr "Rezyume tayyorlash seminarlari"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Learn how to write a clear, professional CV that stands out. Our workshops "
"cover formatting, content, and how to tailor your application for different "
"roles — practical skills you will use throughout your career."
msgstr ""
"Aniq va professional rezyume yozishni o'rganing. Seminarlarimiz formatlash, "
"mazmun va turli lavozimlar uchun arizani qanday moslashtirish kerakligini "
"o'z ichiga oladi — butun karyerangiz davomida foydali amaliy ko'nikmalar."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Interview preparation"
msgstr "Intervyuga tayyorgarlik"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Practice with mock interviews and get honest feedback from our career "
"advisors. We help you prepare answers, build confidence, and learn what "
"hiring managers in Uzbekistan expect from candidates."
msgstr ""
"Sinov intervyular orqali mashq qiling va karyera maslahatchilarimizdan "
"samimiy fikr oling. Biz javoblar tayyorlashda, o'zingizga ishonch hosil "
"qilishda va O'zbekistondagi ish beruvchilar nomzodlardan nimani kutishini "
"o'rganishda yordam beramiz."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid "Career counseling"
msgstr "Karyera bo'yicha maslahat"

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"Not sure which direction to go? Our advisors sit down with you one-on-one to "
"discuss your interests, strengths, and the career paths available to you "
"after graduation."
msgstr ""
"Qaysi yo'nalishni tanlashni bilmayapsizmi? Maslahatchilarimiz siz bilan "
"yakka tartibda suhbatlashib, qiziqishlaringiz, kuchli tomonlaringiz va "
"bitirganingizdan keyin ochiq bo'lgan karyera yo'llarini muhokama qiladi."

#: templates/pages/careers/career-center.html
msgid ""
"We are building relationships with companies across Tashkent and beyond. "
"Through career fairs, guest lectures, and networking events, we connect you "
"directly with employers who are looking for fresh talent."
msgstr ""
"Biz Toshkent va undan tashqaridagi kompaniyalar bilan aloqalar "
"o'rnatmoqdamiz. Karyera yarmarkalari, mehmon ma'ruzalari va networking "
