#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "When can I do an internship?"
msgstr "Amaliyotni qachon o'tashim mumkin?"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"Students can complete internships during the summer break (June–August) or "
"during their final year of study as part of the graduation requirements. The "
"Career Center can help you plan the timing that works best for your schedule."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar amaliyotni yozgi ta'tilda (iyun–avgust) yoki o'qishning yakuniy "
"yilida bitirish talablari doirasida o'tashlari mumkin. Karyera markazi sizga "
"jadvalingizga eng mos vaqtni rejalashtirishda yordam beradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Can I do an internship abroad?"
msgstr "Xorijda amaliyot o'tashim mumkinmi?"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"Yes. The International Relations Department helps students find internship "
"opportunities with our international partner organisations. While the "
"programme is still developing, we are expanding our partnerships each year "
"to offer more options abroad."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Xalqaro aloqalar bo'limi talabalarga xalqaro hamkor tashkilotlarda "
"amaliyot imkoniyatlarini topishda yordam beradi. Dastur hali rivojlanayotgan "
"bo'lsa-da, har yili xorijdagi imkoniyatlarni ko'paytirish uchun "
"hamkorliklarimizni kengaytiryapmiz."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "Do I need to submit an internship report?"
msgstr "Amaliyot hisobotini topshirishim kerakmi?"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"Yes. All students are required to submit an internship report at the end of "
"their placement. Your academic supervisor will provide guidelines on the "
"report format and evaluation criteria."
msgstr ""
"Ha. Barcha talabalar amaliyot yakunida amaliyot hisobotini topshirishlari "
"shart. Ilmiy rahbaringiz hisobot shakli va baholash mezonlari bo'yicha "
"ko'rsatmalar beradi."

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid "How do I find an internship placement?"
msgstr "Amaliyot o'rnini qanday topaman?"

#: templates/pages/careers/internships.html
msgid ""
"Visit the Career Center to browse available placements with our partner "
"companies. You can also propose your own placement — if you have a company "
"in mind, the Career Center can help you formalise the arrangement."
msgstr ""
"Hamkor kompaniyalardagi mavjud amaliyot o'rinlarini ko'rish uchun Karyera "
"markaziga tashrif buyuring. Siz o'zingiz ham amaliyot joyini taklif "
"qilishingiz mumkin — agar nazarda tutgan kompaniyangiz bo'lsa, Karyera "
"markazi kelishuvni rasmiylashtishda yordam beradi."

