#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Why Recruit From TIU?"
msgstr "Nega TIU bitiruvchilarini yollash kerak?"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Tashkent International University produces graduates who are not only "
"academically excellent but also professionally prepared. Our curriculum "
"integrates real-world projects, international standards, and industry "
"partnerships to ensure students are job-ready from day one."
msgstr ""
"TIU nafaqat akademik jihatdan kuchli, balki ko'p tilli va amaliy "
"ko'nikmalarga ega bitiruvchilarni tayyorlaydi. O'quv dasturimiz real "
"loyihalar, xalqaro standartlar va sanoat hamkorligini o'z ichiga oladi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"Our students are fluent in multiple languages including Uzbek, Russian, "
"English, and often a fourth language. They bring diverse perspectives, "
"strong analytical skills, and a global mindset to every organization they "
"join."
msgstr ""
"Talabalarimiz o'zbek, rus, ingliz va boshqa tillarni biladi. Ular har bir "
"tashkilotga xilma-xil nuqtai nazar, kuchli tahliliy ko'nikmalar va global "
"tafakkurni olib keladi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
"With programs spanning Business & Economics, IT & Engineering, Law, and "
"Humanities, we offer a broad talent pool across disciplines. Our Career "
"Center team works directly with employers to understand hiring needs and "
"match the right candidates."
msgstr ""
"Biznes, IT, Huquq va Gumanitar fanlar bo'yicha dasturlarimiz keng iqtidor "
"havzasini taklif etadi. Karyera markazimiz ish beruvchilar bilan bevosita "
"ishlaydi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "What Sets Us Apart"
msgstr "Bizni ajratib turadigan narsa"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "International Curriculum"
msgstr "Xalqaro o'quv dasturi"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
