"taught by faculty from leading universities worldwide."
msgstr ""
"Global standartlarga mos dasturlar, xalqaro akkreditatsiya va dunyoning "
"yetakchi universitetlaridan kelgan o'qituvchilar."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid "Multilingual Graduates"
msgstr "Ko'p tilli bitiruvchilar"

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
msgid ""
