"multinational teams and global operations."
msgstr ""
"Talabalar kamida uchta tilni biladi, bu ularni ko'p millatli jamoalar va "
"global operatsiyalar uchun ideal qiladi."

#: templates/pages/careers/employer-partnerships.html
